NG0249:1: [(]1[)]@#// rta mchog rol pa'i rgyud chen po bzhugs so //
NG0249:4: shrihha ya gri wa la li ta ma ha tan+t+ra /
NG0249:6: rta mchog rol pa'i rgyud chen po /
NG0249:7: bcom ldan 'das dpal pad+ma dbang chen he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0249:8: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na //
NG0249:9: bcom ldan 'das dbang gi rgyal po /
NG0249:10: dus gsum ma lus mi lus lus pa med pa'i ngo bo /
NG0249:11: pad+ma dang rdo rje dang 'khor lo dang rin chen dang */
NG0249:12: las kyi rigs kyi rang bzhin /
NG0249:13: rigs dang ye shes kyi bdag nyid /
NG0249:14: rol pa'i rdzu 'phrul la mnga' brnyes pa des /
NG0249:15: don chos nyid skye ba med pa las /
NG0249:16: rtags 'gag pa med pa cho 'phrul gyi skur bzhugs so //
NG0249:17: 'og min gyi gnas gsang ba dbang gi gnas chen po na /
NG0249:18: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams gshegs shing bzhugs te zhugs par gyur pa'i gnas //
NG0249:21: dur khrod la byas pa'i dbyibs dang */
NG0249:22: kha dog tha dad cing ngo bo nyid gcig pa ste //
NG0249:23: de yang dbyings las ye shes gsal ba'i gzhal yas khang */
NG0249:24: kun tu khyab par gdal ba chen po na /
NG0249:27: gzhal yang sems dpa' dang sems ma dang */
NG0249:28: sgo skyong sprul skur bcas pa yang sri zhu dang rim gro ba'i tshul gyis /
NG0249:29: til la mar bzhin khyab par gnas so //
NG0249:31: pad+ma las kyi sems dpa' nyid /
NG0249:32: nyid kyi sku gsung thugs las thon te /
NG0249:33: spyan snga nyid na bka' nod pa'i spobs pa dang ldan pa'i zhu ba po nyid du bzhugs so //
NG0249:34: rta mchog rol pa'i rgyud las gleng gzhi'i le'u ste dang po'o ///
NG0249:35: / de nas dbang gi rgyal po chen po des /
NG0249:36: dus gsum dang srid pa gsum dang */
NG0249:37: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad la /
NG0249:38: rdzu 'phrul gyi spyan gyis khyab par gzigs so //
NG0249:40: chos thams cad byang chub kyi sems kyi mtshan nyid /
NG0249:41: stong pa chen po'i rang bzhin /
NG0249:42: smra bsam las 'das pa'i de bzhin nyid du de
NG0249:43: kho na'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs so
NG0249:44: // de nas pad+ma las kyi sems dpa' de rang gi stan las langs te /
NG0249:45: bcom ldan 'das dbang gi rgyal po la /
NG0249:46: phyi nang gi mchod pa'i sprin sna tshogs kyis mchod de lan brgya phrag stong du phyag 'tshal nas /
NG0249:47: dgongs pa chos kyi dbyings la mnal bzhin du /
NG0249:49: e ma dbang mchog gsang ba'i bdag / dkyil 'khor rnams kyi de bzhin don //
NG0249:50: byang chub sems kyi mtshan nyid de //
NG0249:51: bdag la sogs la bshad du gsol //
NG0249:52: de nas dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0249:53: pad+ma las kyi sems dpa' nyon cig / khyod kyis zhu bar spobs pa legs so //
NG0249:54: legs par yid la zung zhig / 'di ni sngon gyi rgyal ba thams cad dang */
NG0249:55: da ltar dang phyis 'byung ba'i rgyal ba rnams kyis
NG0249:56: ma gsungs gsung bar mi 'gyur zhing dka' ba yin
NG0249:57: te / de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NG0249:58: de kho na nyid byang chub sems kyi mtshan nyid de ni brjod du'ang med la /
NG0249:59: snod du gyur pa dkon pa'i phyir ro //
NG0249:60: khyod kyis nga la dris shig / ces bka' stsal te /
NG0249:63: de nas 'khor ris med kyis pad+ma sems dpa' la bsgo ba mdzad do //
NG0249:64: 'gro ba rnams la snod ji lta ba bzhin du chos ston cing */
NG0249:65: byang chub sems dpa' blo dman pa rnams la byin gyis rlobs shing */
NG0249:66: sangs rgyas rnams kyis bskul ba dbang gi rgyal po'i thugs su chud de /
NG0249:67: ston pa'i zhal du bltas te gnas so //
NG0249:68: de nas pad+ma las kyi sems dpas /
NG0249:69: ma chags pa'i mchod pas mchod nas /
NG0249:70: dbang gi rgyal po la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:71: don dam sems nyid skye ba med pa la //
NG0249:72: ston pa dang ni gnas dang 'khor //
NG0249:76: chos kun sems kyi rtsa ba ste //
NG0249:77: rtsa ba de nyid ston pa las //
NG0249:78: gud nas ston pas stsal ba min //
NG0249:79: bdag nyid chen po byang chub sems //
NG0249:80: rgyu dang 'bras bur bcas pa'i chos //
NG0249:81: byang chub sems la gnas pa las //
NG0249:82: gud na gnas pa ma yin no //
NG0249:83: de bzhin gzhal yas byang chub sems //
NG0249:84: 'khor ba'i gru rten phung po lnga //
NG0249:85: 'khor ba gnas gyur phyag rgya yin //
NG0249:86: phyag rgya de nyid byang chub sems //
NG0249:87: 'byung ba gnas gyur yum lnga ste //
NG0249:88: yum lnga ma chags byang chub sems //
NG0249:89: rnam shes 'khor ba gnas gyur byang chub sems //
NG0249:90: yul brgyad 'khor ba gnas gyur sems ma ste //
NG0249:91: gnas pa med pa'i byang chub sems //
NG0249:92: reg bya reg byed gnas gyur khro bo'o //
NG0249:93: rtag chad gnas gyur sgo srung ste //
NG0249:94: smon pa med pa'i byang chub sems //
NG0249:95: yid ches kun bzang yab yum ste //
NG0249:96: nyon mongs gnas gyur sprul sku drug / gzung 'dzin med pa'i byang chub sems //
NG0249:97: 'khrul pa bzlog phyir shar ba las //
NG0249:98: gud nas stsal ba ma yin no //
NG0249:99: rtsa ba de nyid rtogs pa na //
NG0249:100: cir yang ma bkag chos kyi dbyings //
NG0249:101: lta ba ma bkag sems nyid yin //
NG0249:102: spyod pa ma bkag rgya mtsho yin //
NG0249:103: bsgrub pa ma bkag sems nyid bsgrub //
NG0249:104: phrin las ma bkag sems kyis kun la rol //
NG0249:105: dam tshig ma bkag sems la bsrung du med //
NG0249:106: mchod pa ma bkag sems las longs spyod pa'o //
NG0249:107: snying po ma bkag sems nyid brjod dang bral //
NG0249:108: sems nyid ma bkag sangs rgya'o //
NG0249:109: ting 'dzin ma bkag ngang la shar //
NG0249:110: 'khor rnams mtshan ma med pa las //
NG0249:111: mtshan ma 'byung ba rtag pa'i sku sel to //
NG0249:112: de nas 'khor rnams byang chub sems la 'khod de
NG0249:113: stong pa'i ngang las zhi ba'i skur bzhengs te 'gro
NG0249:115: dus gsum gyi 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa rgyu dang 'bras bur bcas pa rnams /
NG0249:116: stong pa chen por gyur pa ni /
NG0249:117: dpe nam mkha'i mtshan nyid tsam du yang */
NG0249:118: rgyun du yod pa ma yin no //
NG0249:119: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:120: byang chub kyi sems de kho na nyid kyi le'u
NG0249:121: ste gnyis pa'o // // de nas las kyi sems
NG0249:123: bcom ldan 'das dbang gi rgyal po la 'di skad ces gsol @#//
NG0249:125: las kyi sems dpa' chen po'i 'khor //
NG0249:126: 'gro ba ji snyed dad pa las //
NG0249:127: ma dad par ni gyur pa yi //
NG0249:128: las kyi log lta ma dad pa //
NG0249:129: rgyu dang rkyen ni gang las byung *//
NG0249:130: ma dad pa ni ci yi phyir //
NG0249:131: rigs dang sde ni gang du gtogs //
NG0249:132: 'bras bu smin pa ji ltar lags //
NG0249:134: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0249:135: dka' thub can gyi sems can de //
NG0249:136: legs pa'i rgyu las ma byung ste //
NG0249:137: med pa'i gzung 'dzin rtog ngan rgyu //
NG0249:138: rkyen ni chags sdang la sogs te //
NG0249:139: lta ba log pa nyon mongs lnga //
NG0249:140: de yi las kyi dbang btsan nas //
NG0249:141: 'bras bu ma dad rgyu ru smin //
NG0249:142: rigs ni 'khor ba'i rigs can de //
NG0249:143: de ni 'byung po'i rigs su gtogs //
NG0249:144: pad+ma las kyi sems dpa' des yang gsol pa /
NG0249:145: bcom ldan 'das dbang gi rgyal po /
NG0249:146: ma dad de ni ji ltar 'dul //
NG0249:147: btul nas yon tan ji ltar thob //
NG0249:148: ma btul ba yi skyon ni ci //
NG0249:150: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0249:151: log lta mthu bsnyems sems can de //
NG0249:152: bden pa'i gzhung gis gdul bar bya //
NG0249:153: ma btul ba yi skyon bstan pa //
NG0249:154: phyin ci log tu chos spyad nas //
NG0249:155: lha dang mi yi srid brlags te //
NG0249:156: don las nyams pa'i skyon yod do //
NG0249:157: dug gsum rtsad bcad 'khor dong sprug / sangs rgyas zhing khams rab tu rgyas //
NG0249:158: de nas zhi bas 'dul bar gzigs pas /
NG0249:159: ru tra nag po des se gol lan cig brdabs pas /
NG0249:160: mi 'dul ba'i nga rgyal skyes te /
NG0249:161: gau ta ma khyod kyis bdag 'dul ba ni ma lags te /
NG0249:162: rang rang gnas su dka' thub la dengs shig /
NG0249:163: ces smra zhing kha t+wam ga 'khrol zhing ma nyan
NG0249:164: to // rta mchog rol pa'i rgyud chen po las /
NG0249:165: ma dad pa'i sems can chen po zhi bas 'dul
NG0249:166: bar gzigs pas ma thul ba'i le'u ste gsum pa'o
NG0249:167: // // de nas rigs lnga rdo rje'i rigs dang
NG0249:171: las kyi rigs dang bcas pa rnams kyis zhi bas ma thul nas /
NG0249:173: rdo rje rigs kyis bgros pa /
NG0249:174: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung na //
NG0249:175: bdag nyid chen po rtag pa ni //
NG0249:176: de tshe sems can thams cad ni //
NG0249:177: shin tu khro zhing gtum par gyur //
NG0249:178: shin tu khro zhing gtum pa la //
NG0249:179: zhi bas phan par ma gyur te //
NG0249:180: shes rab thabs kyi rnal 'byor pas //
NG0249:181: khro bo de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
NG0249:182: khro bo'i tshul chen khros pas kyang *//
NG0249:183: 'jig rten gsum dag bsreg byed na //
NG0249:184: sangs rgyas thams cad khros pa yis //
NG0249:185: khams gsum ma lus dbang sdud na //
NG0249:186: ma dad sems can smos ci dgos //
NG0249:188: de nas rin chen rigs kyis bgros pa /
NG0249:189: kye ma 'dus pa'i tshogs chen rnams //
NG0249:190: las kyi mnar ba'i dus zad 'dis //
NG0249:191: 'khor ba gtan gyi gzhi byas nas //
NG0249:192: phyi rabs rnams kyang g.yang sar bsgyur //
NG0249:196: de nas de bzhin rigs kyis bgros pa /
NG0249:197: kye ma sems can sangs rgyas tshogs can rnams //
NG0249:198: ma dad sems can chen po 'di //
NG0249:199: sngon gyi sa bon rtsub mos 'phangs //
NG0249:200: nyon mongs lnga ru smin pa ste //
NG0249:201: nyon mongs bdud kyi rgyu ru smin //
NG0249:204: de nas pad+ma'i rigs kyis bgros pa /
NG0249:205: kye ma gsang mchog gsang ba'i tshogs //
NG0249:206: ma dad pa yi sems can 'di //
NG0249:207: nyon mongs bdud kyi gzhi byas te //
NG0249:208: srid pa ma lus g.yang sar bsgyur //
NG0249:211: de nas las kyi rigs kyis bgros pa /
NG0249:212: kye ma sangs rgyas tshogs chen rnams //
NG0249:213: ma dad pa yi sems can 'di //
NG0249:214: nyon mongs dug gsum bzhi byas te //
NG0249:215: thams cad ma lus brlag par byed //
NG0249:216: 'khor ba bsgral ba'i dus la bab //
NG0249:218: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:219: bde bar gshegs pas bka' bgros pa'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o ///
NG0249:221: dbang gi rgyal po la sogs pa rigs lnga dgongs pa gcig tu gyur te /
NG0249:222: log pa'i spyod pa can ru tra la sogs pa
NG0249:223: gdug pa can thams cad sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa
NG0249:224: la mngon par ma dad pa /
NG0249:225: 'jig rten phung bar byed pa rnams //
NG0249:226: zhi bas phan pa'i skabs la ma bab ste /
NG0249:227: rol ba'i mdzad spyod kyis 'dul bar gzigs te thams cad dgongs pa gcig tu gyur to //
NG0249:228: de nas dbang gi rgyal pos /
NG0249:229: hum hum hum zhes brjod pas /
NG0249:230: dkyil 'khor thams cad bdag la bsdu bar mdzad de gnyis su med par gnas so //
NG0249:231: stong pa nyid kyi ngang las dgongs te /
NG0249:232: snying rje chen po tsam la brten /
NG0249:233: 'dzin rtog zil gyis gnon pa'i ting nge 'dzin mngon par 'du mdzad de /
NG0249:234: mtshan ma rgyu'i snying po yi ge hum dmar po ye shes kyi 'od du 'bar te /
NG0249:235: snod kyi 'jig rten gzhal yas khang du shar bar mdzad pa'i phyir /
NG0249:236: mi rtog pa'i hum dmar po de las /
NG0249:237: cho 'phrul gyi sgra 'di rnams brjod do /
NG0249:238: sngags rnams sor bzhag / e ma de wa tram
NG0249:239: ma man+dal kro ta dz+wa la ram hum yam hum
NG0249:240: yam / ma ha rak+ta dz+wa mun ta man+da la /
NG0249:241: keng ni ri ti dz+wa la man+da la karma ma tish+tha rag sha hum b+h+rum /
NG0249:242: de nas 'byung ba rim du shar //
NG0249:243: zhe sdang 'bar ba'i nam mkha' la //
NG0249:246: gti mug chen po'i sa gzhi la //
NG0249:247: nga rgyal chen po'i me ri 'bar //
NG0249:248: dbang chen 'byung bar shar bar mdzad //
NG0249:249: nang dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang du shar bar mdzad /
NG0249:250: 'khor rnams bskyed de btul nas bsgral bar gzas pas /
NG0249:251: ma dad pa chen po de /
NG0249:253: chags pa'i rgya mtsho gting nas g.yos /
NG0249:254: mun pa'i kha rlangs sprin ltar gtibs /
NG0249:255: phrag dog gi zug rngu ni bslang */
NG0249:256: nga rgyal gyi de'u bskyed de /
NG0249:258: ru lu dang kha tam ga 'khrol zhing rtsogs par gzo ba las /
NG0249:259: dbang gi rgyal pos gdug pa'i lag cha phrogs /
NG0249:260: kho'i nyon mongs pa'i sgra ru lu ni /
NG0249:261: om dang hum gi bar du bcug ste /
NG0249:262: om ru lu ru lu hum zhes bzlas pas /
NG0249:263: dregs pa can de skyes bu lce bcad pa bzhin nyams so //
NG0249:269: shig shig phrug cig / a hu a hu /
NG0249:274: drag po'i sngags des brgyab pas /
NG0249:275: lus dum bu bcu gsum du bshig / dur khrod
NG0249:276: brgyad du bshig go / khog pa gzhal yas khang
NG0249:277: du byas so // chung ma la sogs pa thams cad 'khor du byas te sbyor ro //
NG0249:278: dang po de nyid du grags pa las /
NG0249:279: stong pa'i cho 'phrul gyi sgra 'di brjod do //
NG0249:280: shu n+ya ta dz+nya na at+ma ko\u0f85ham /
NG0249:281: rnam par mi rtog ye nas skye med cing *//
NG0249:282: gzung 'dzin rtog med mtha' gnyis ma chags dbyings //
NG0249:283: ye nas mnyam nyid rang bzhin ji bzhin dang *//
NG0249:284: rnam rtog spros bral smra bsam brjod las 'das //
NG0249:285: stong pa'i ngang las snying rje shar //
NG0249:286: kun tu snang ba'i sgra ni brjod //
NG0249:288: ma ltar byams pas kun la khyab pa'i sku //
NG0249:289: mkha' ltar dag pa cho 'phrul 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NG0249:290: kun la snyoms pa'i ye shes gsal ba'i ngang *//
NG0249:291: yon tan rin chen 'byung ba dbang ldan yum //
NG0249:292: de nas 'bras bu hum dmar la dngas pa byung ste /
NG0249:293: de las skul ba'i sgra 'di byung ngo *//
NG0249:294: yi ge hum ni sems kyi rang bzhin te //
NG0249:295: chags pa'i skyon bral pad+ma ra ga'i mdog / sangs rgyas che ba'i khyad par bstan pa'i phyir //
NG0249:296: rgya mtsho'i rlabs ltar khro bo'i sprul pa 'byung *//
NG0249:298: de nas gzhal yas sku dang */
NG0249:302: hum dmar po las yi ge 'phros /
NG0249:304: phyi rin po che la nang dur khrod 'bar ba /
NG0249:306: phyi nas bltas na nang gsal /
NG0249:307: nang nas bltas na phyi gsal bar bskyed /
NG0249:308: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyis byin gyis brlabs /
NG0249:311: mu khyud bar khyams sgo khyud du bcas par bsam /
NG0249:313: hum dmar la bkra ba ni bsam /
NG0249:316: pad+ma shri he ru ka / ma ha ro sha /
NG0249:317: kha la ro sha / hri ram hri ram /
NG0249:319: a si mu sal pra ban shu ken /
NG0249:324: bi lang ku sha la s+t+wam /
NG0249:325: ban tri sha / pad+ma gal sha kha'i /
NG0249:328: kha kha rad na gu h+ya dz+nya na sid+d+hi /
NG0249:330: dza lam dza lam badzra hum /
NG0249:331: sum b+ha ni sum b+ha ni hum phat /
NG0249:332: kro ta rag sha ru lu ru lu hum phat /
NG0249:333: zhes pas che ba'i nga rgyal brjod cing */
NG0249:335: dbang chen pad+ma he ru ka dbu lnga pa /
NG0249:338: dmar po brgyad nas zhabs brgyad byung ba /
NG0249:339: rdo rje lcags kyu sbrul gyi zhags pa bsnams //
NG0249:340: be con rnge'u chung shel gyi rnge'u chung bsnams //
NG0249:341: thod rlon khrag dang sdigs mdzub mdzad //
NG0249:342: sbrul nag zhags pa bsnams pa ste //
NG0249:343: rdo rje'i gshog pa g.yas g.yon du gdengs pa'o //
NG0249:344: rta mgo ljang gu lnga byung ba'o //
NG0249:345: ma dad pa chen po tshul dang bstun te bsgral lo //
NG0249:346: rang gis rang la yi ge hum la bstod pa /
NG0249:347: hum hum gis srid gsum ma lus dbang du sdud /
NG0249:348: hum gis ngan song gnas rnams stongs par mdzad //
NG0249:349: hum gis ma rigs mun khang gtan nas 'joms //
NG0249:350: hum gis thams cad 'jigs shing thams cad dbang du sdud //
NG0249:351: hum gis dus gsum rgyal ba'i sku yang bskyed //
NG0249:352: hum gis bla med byang chub gnas su sgrol //
NG0249:353: hum mdzad hum gi lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0249:354: de nas rang gi che ba'i nga rgyal 'di brjod do //
NG0249:355: sku bzhi gcig tu bsdus pas kun tu zhal //
NG0249:356: phyogs bzhi rigs bzhir 'bar ba'i skur bstan pas //
NG0249:357: spyi mthun lnga lngar snang ba nam mkha'i rgyan du ston //
NG0249:358: rigs kyi dbang rnams rdzogs pas thams cad ma lus dbang du sdud //
NG0249:359: hum mdzad khro bo chen po brgyad kyi snying *//
NG0249:360: chad par bcug nas nang dang bsres te gsol //
NG0249:361: byams dang snying rjer ldan pa'i tshul mnga' bas //
NG0249:362: rdo rje lcags kyu sbrul gyi zhags pa dang *//
NG0249:363: be con rnge'u chung b+han+d+ha shel gyi rnge'u chung 'dzin //
NG0249:364: thod rlon khrag dang bsres pa gsol //
NG0249:365: phyogs bzhir hum gi rgyun du sgra sgrags pas //
NG0249:366: rdo rje byin chen 'bar ba gsor zhing brdeg / gdu bu dbu rgyan sbrul nag mi srun pa //
NG0249:367: hum gi sgra grags bskal pa'i me chen 'bar //
NG0249:368: sdigs pa'i rtse la bskal pa'i me 'bar bas //
NG0249:369: ma rig rmongs pa'i mun nag sel //
NG0249:370: mi ldog sa la 'gro ba 'dren pa'i rtags //
NG0249:371: thabs kyi zhags pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud //
NG0249:372: rdo rje rin chen las byung gshog pa ni //
NG0249:373: nyi ma 'bum gyis brgyan pa'i the'u gshog can //
NG0249:374: zhi rgyas dbang drag phrin las mngon spyod kyis //
NG0249:375: thams cad bla med byang chub gnas su grol ba'o //
NG0249:376: ting 'dzin zil gyis gnon pa stag gi chas //
NG0249:377: rno gdug zlog byed rgya bye'u lcags kyi chas //
NG0249:378: shes rab ting 'dzin rdo rje bcas pa'i chas //
NG0249:379: dbang gi bswe khrab smug po gzi 'bar bgrad pa'i chas //
NG0249:380: dpa' brjid mnyen lcug sbrul nag rgyan gyis brgyan //
NG0249:381: dmar gsal dbang sdud ting 'dzin che ba'i mchog / mnyen lcug chun 'phyang dar gyi chas //
NG0249:382: sdug bsngal nyam thag skad chen 'byin //
NG0249:383: om na sha stam pa ni /
NG0249:386: zhes che ba'i sgo nas nyid la bstod pa'o //
NG0249:388: om a ka de big de ka ra ka ra ga te swa mam zhes brjod pas /
NG0249:389: yum gzi ldan pad+ma can rgyan dang cha lugs gtso dang mthun pa la /
NG0249:390: tshul mo bag tu gnas pa zhig bskyed do //
NG0249:391: g.yas na yid bzhin nor bu bsnams pa /

NG0249:845: dbus zlum 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad la //
NG0249:846: de yi tha ma pad+ma brgyad dang ldan //
NG0249:847: phyi ma sgo la sgo khyud ni //
NG0249:848: gsang ba dbang gi dkyil 'khor ro //
NG0249:849: nub kyi zla gum sgo gcig pa //
NG0249:850: phyi rim zlum po dag gis bskor //
NG0249:851: de yi phyi rim khyud kyis bskor //
NG0249:852: phyi ma gru bzhi sgo dang bcas //
NG0249:853: de la dbang gi lha bkod pa //
NG0249:854: dbang bskur thabs kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NG0249:855: dbus ni gru bzhi lham pa la //
NG0249:856: zlum pos mtha' bskor bar khyams sgo dang bcas //
NG0249:857: dbang gi las bzhi'i dkyil 'khor yin //
NG0249:858: zlum po gcig la tshom bu lnga //
NG0249:859: ye shes dbang gi lha gsal ba //
NG0249:860: bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor chen por gsungs //
NG0249:861: rta mchog rol pa'i tan tra las /
NG0249:862: dkyil 'khor rnam par spros pa'i le'u ste bcu pa'o ///
NG0249:863: / de nas yang byang chub las kyi sems dpas /
NG0249:864: dbang gi rgyal po la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:865: kye ma dbang mchog dbang gi bdag / gsang sngags dam pa bshad du gsol //
NG0249:867: dbang gi rgyal po sngags dang phyag rgya rnam par spros pa'i ting nge 'dzin la zhugs te /
NG0249:868: hum hum zhes sgra byung ste /
NG0249:869: hum badzra d+h+r-ika / mum d+ha twi shwa ri /
NG0249:870: om dzi na dzika / lam dwe sha ra ti /
NG0249:871: swa rat+na d+h+r-ika / mam mo ha ra ti /
NG0249:872: am a ro lika / pyam ra ga ra ti /
NG0249:873: ha pra dz+nya d+h+r-ika / ham badzra ra ti /
NG0249:874: bud+d+ha ya ta so ta a ham /
NG0249:875: badzra ya ta sta tha pra ta a ha~m rat+na ya ta tha tra a ham /
NG0249:876: pad+ma ya ta sta ta swa a ham /
NG0249:877: karma ya ta sta tha so ta a ham /
NG0249:878: rigs lnga yab yum dzahhum bam hoh //
NG0249:879: rigs re re la yang lha mo bzhi bzhis bskor ba'o //
NG0249:890: sr-i ga la mu khi he /
NG0249:897: ha ya gri wa d+hi d+hi gan d+ha ho //
NG0249:898: du ru du ru tsha mi b+h+yo /
NG0249:899: kha yang ku ku sa ma ya dza /
NG0249:900: ku la sa ma ya dza du /
NG0249:901: brtul zhugs bzhi yis rnam par spros //
NG0249:902: badzra shwa na mu kha dza ma na ya /
NG0249:904: om badzra a mo ka hi ta sha dza /
NG0249:907: gsang ba'i yum chen mo bzhi'o //
NG0249:908: ma te sha ra ram pa ni /
NG0249:910: d+hi dam ma a sha ma /
NG0249:912: shwa ti kha la dun tri dza ya /
NG0249:914: rak+sha kra ma sang tre yam /
NG0249:916: om ru lu ru lu bam ta sa ma ya trig sham kha la ma b+h+yo /
NG0249:917: kham brgya ma drug gi 'thon to //
NG0249:918: gar dza ha na bin d+ha tsakra da pa la /
NG0249:922: sgo'i khro bo rnams kyi 'thon no //
NG0249:923: de rnams kyi sgo so sor 'thon no //
NG0249:924: hum ru lu ru lu phat e a ra li hri dza /
NG0249:925: zhes pa 'di ni dril ba'i gnas kyi snying po'o //
NG0249:926: de nas las ma lus par gsungs @#//
NG0249:928: rta mchog rol pa'i tan tra las /
NG0249:929: gsang sngags rnams spros pa'i le'u ste bcu gcig pa'o ///
NG0249:930: / de nas yang phyag rgya rnam thar spros te /
NG0249:931: rnam par grol bas sgrol ba mtshon pa'i phyir /
NG0249:933: dbu lnga phyag kyang bcu drug ste //
NG0249:934: dbu la rmad du byung ba ni //
NG0249:935: ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin te //
NG0249:936: shar du gzigs pa'i dbu mchog ni //
NG0249:937: dri za'i rgyal po gnon pa'i dgu //
NG0249:938: lho ru gzigs pa'i dbu mchog ni /
NG0249:939: gshin rje'i rgyal po 'joms pa'i dbu //
NG0249:940: nub tu gzigs pa'i dbu mchog ni //
NG0249:941: klu dbang rgyal po gzir ba'i dbu //
NG0249:942: byang du gzigs pa'i dbu mchog ni //
NG0249:943: gnod sbyin mya ngan skyed pa'i dbu //
NG0249:944: dbus ni bdud bzhi 'dul ba'i dbu //
NG0249:945: lhang lhang 'tsher 'tsher phyogs bcur rta skad 'tsher //
NG0249:946: sangs rgyas 'dus shing gar gyi phyag rgyar gsal //
NG0249:947: g.yas pa brgyad kyis nyon mongs brgyad rnams sgrol zhing ye shes brgyad du ston //
NG0249:948: g.yon pas bsgral nas pha rol phyin bcur sbyor //
NG0249:949: rdo rje'i gshog pas khams gsum sa rnams gnon //
NG0249:950: zhabs brgyad bgrad pas dug lnga tshogs brgyad 'joms //
NG0249:951: dpal chen dbang gi rgyal po ni //
NG0249:952: 'bar ba'i gdan las bzhengs nas kyang *//
NG0249:953: ye shes 'phrul gyi dngos grub stsol //
NG0249:954: phyag rgya g.yas brkyang g.yon mnan te //
NG0249:955: lan gsum bsgyur cing mkha' la dgrol //
NG0249:956: phyag rgya'i mchod pa chen por gsungs //
NG0249:957: rta mchog rol pa'i tan tra las /
NG0249:958: phyag rgya rnam par spros pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis
NG0249:959: pa'o // // de nas yang las kyi sems dpas
NG0249:960: / pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug la /
NG0249:961: lha rnams rgyan dang cha lugs bshad du gsol //
NG0249:963: dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0249:964: dbang gi rgyal po las dang skabs dbye na //
NG0249:965: las dang rnam pa 'di ltar gsungs //
NG0249:966: dur khrod gar gyi bdag po ni //
NG0249:968: phyag rgya drug tu gsal lo //
NG0249:969: tram dmar po brgyad la zhabs dmar po brgyad du bgrad do //
NG0249:971: stag lpags zhing gi pags pa dang */
NG0249:975: de ltar mche ba gtsigs pa /
NG0249:976: rdo rje'i gshog pas kun tu gtams pa /
NG0249:977: gzi ldan pad+ma yab dang mthun par gsal ba'o //
NG0249:978: ma las gsang ba'i yum chen mo //
NG0249:979: sku tshon rin po che sna tshogs su 'bar ba'o //
NG0249:980: phyag na gsang ba'i thod pa re bsnams pa'o //
NG0249:981: li las long ba sum cu rtsa gnyis byung ngo *//
NG0249:983: sku ni rin chen 'bar ba las /
NG0249:984: phyag na shel gyi 'khar ba bsnams pa //
NG0249:985: chibs su stag mo brgyad la chibs pa /
NG0249:986: dbu la sprul pa char du 'bebs //
NG0249:987: dung gi a long khra la la //
NG0249:988: lho yi phyogs nas long ba brgyad //
NG0249:989: sku ni rin chen 'bar ba la //
NG0249:990: phyag na gser gyi 'khar ba bsnams //
NG0249:991: dbu la rin chen thog chen 'bebs //
NG0249:992: chibs su chu srin brgyad la
NG0249:995: gser gyi a long khra la la //
NG0249:996: nub nas long ba brgyad byung ste //
NG0249:997: rin chen 'bar ba'i sku lus la //
NG0249:998: phyag na byu ru'i 'khar ba bsnams //
NG0249:999: ba glang dmar po brgyad la chibs //
NG0249:1000: dbu la thog rgod char ltar 'bebs //
NG0249:1001: byu ru dmar po'i a long 'khrol //
NG0249:1002: byang nas long ba brgyad byung ste //
NG0249:1003: rin chen 'bar ba'i sku lus la //
NG0249:1004: phyag na g.yu yi 'khar ba bsnams //
NG0249:1005: chibs su khyung chen brgyad la chibs //
NG0249:1006: rin chen 'bar ba'i a long can //
NG0249:1007: dbu la thog chen char chen 'bebs //
NG0249:1008: dbang chen pad+ma'i bka' la sdod //
NG0249:1009: sti brgyad las spyang mo brgyad la //
NG0249:1010: byu ru dmar po'i a long re re yod pa /
NG0249:1012: tshig chad kha gdangs dza brgyad las kyi brgyad byung ste //
NG0249:1013: dung gi khyi gser gyi khyi zangs kyi khyi /
NG0249:1015: ral pa mda' tshad shar re 'dug pa /
NG0249:1017: byu ru'i a long la dza dmar po re re yod pa byung ngo *//
NG0249:1018: dza sum cu rtsa drug las /
NG0249:1019: pho nya mgo brnyan mang po byung ngo *//
NG0249:1020: b+h+yo b+h+yo brgya rtsa brgyad las /
NG0249:1021: sing ha dzam b+ha la b+h+yo /
NG0249:1022: zhes brgya rtsa brgyad brjod pas /
NG0249:1023: gser gyi seng ge nyi shu rtsa brgya yin nam brgyad la /
NG0249:1026: ske na byu ru dmar po'i a long re yod pa /
NG0249:1027: b+h+yo re la a long re la yi ge b+h+yo //
NG0249:1028: dmar po re yod pa de ltar byung ngo *//
NG0249:1029: dza las pho nya mgo brnyan ma drug cu rtsa gnyis byung ngo *//
NG0249:1032: byi la'i mgo can rnams dang */
NG0249:1033: gcan gzan gdug pa'i mgo can rnams dang */
NG0249:1034: khyi spyang la sogs pa'i mgo can mang po byung ngo *//
NG0249:1035: gzhan yang gdug pa'i mgo bo can mang po la byu ru'i a long dang */
NG0249:1038: a long can mang po yang dbang gi rgyal po la bltas te gnas so //
NG0249:1041: ti ra phra mo mdzes pa'i tshul can no //
NG0249:1042: ti ra gnas nyul ma zhes bya ste /
NG0249:1043: bud med mi bzad gdug pa'i cha lugs can /
NG0249:1044: zhing gi dbyug pa lag na thogs pa /
NG0249:1045: ti ra phra mo kha nas khyer te rgyug pa /
NG0249:1046: za byed sha khrag gi bdag mor bzhugs so //
NG0249:1047: a ra las dmus long brgyad dung gi khyi mo
NG0249:1048: byu ru'i khol thag can brgyad la zhon nas rjes
NG0249:1050: long ba la zangs kyi zhags pa dang */
NG0249:1051: khrag gi par bu thogs te dbang gi rgyal po'i bka' nyan cing */
NG0249:1053: gzhan yang 'khor mang pos bskor te bzhugs so //
NG0249:1054: shar gyi mgo dgu brtsegs pa ni /
NG0249:1056: lho'i mgo bdun brtsegs pa ni zangs kyi zhags pa bsnams pa'o //
NG0249:1057: nub kyi mgo lnga brtsegs pa ni /
NG0249:1058: lcags sgrog tho ba bsnams pa'o //
NG0249:1059: byang gi mgo gsum brtsegs pa ni /
NG0249:1061: rta mchog rol pa'i tan tra las /
NG0249:1062: 'khor rnams bskyed cing spros pa'i le'u ste @#//
NG0249:1063: bcu gsum pa'o //    // de nas yang dbang gi rgyal po des /
NG0249:1064: gnas lnga nas yi ge lnga bton te /
NG0249:1066: spyi bo bde ba chen po'i gzhal yas khang nas /
NG0249:1067: om dkar po las hu lu hu lu phat e a ra li hum hrihdzahsa bskor ba'o //
NG0249:1068: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo'i gzhal yas nas /
NG0249:1069: am las yi ge hu lu hu lu phat e a ra li hum hrihdzahsa bskor ba'o //
NG0249:1070: tsit+ta rin po che'i gzhal yas khang nas /
NG0249:1071: hum mthing ga la hu lu hu lu phat /
NG0249:1072: e a ra li hum hrih dzahsa bskor ba'o //
NG0249:1073: lte ba sprul pa'i gzhal yas nas /
NG0249:1074: swa ser po las hu lu hu lu hum phat /
NG0249:1075: e a ra li hum hrihdzahsa bskor ba'o //
NG0249:1076: gsang ba'i gnas kyi me rlung las kyi gzhal yas nas /
NG0249:1077: ha ljang gu la yi ge hu lu hu lu hum phat e a ra li hrihdzahsa bskor ba'o //
NG0249:1078: bde chen 'khor lo 'dab ma sum cu gnyis /
NG0249:1079: mgrin pa longs spyod 'khor lo 'dab ma bcu drug / tsit+ta chos kyi 'khor lo 'dab ma brgyad /
NG0249:1080: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo drug cu rtsa bzhi /
NG0249:1081: me rlung 'khor lo gzhu dang ba dan dbyibs /
NG0249:1082: dngos po'i gnas lugs de ltar gsungs /
NG0249:1083: de nas bsdus pa 'bru brgya spros /
NG0249:1084: de las spros dang bsdus pa'i /
NG0249:1085: lha rnams rdzogs pa gsang ba'i snying po'i don /
NG0249:1086: dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsal to //
NG0249:1087: dang po zhi ba'i bsnyen pa dbul //
NG0249:1088: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor la'o //
NG0249:1089: bde gshegs thugs mnyes 'gro ba'i sgrib pa sbyong *//
NG0249:1090: om ni rigs lnga yab yum snying po'o //
NG0249:1091: hu lu gong ma sems dpa' brgyad du ste //
NG0249:1093: phat ni mchod pa'i lha mo ste //
NG0249:1094: e dang a ra li ni thub pa drug / hum ni sgo ma chen mo bzhi //
NG0249:1095: hrihdzahgnyis ni kun bzang yab yum sngags //
NG0249:1096: de ltar zhi ba bsgrub par gsungs //
NG0249:1097: de nas khro bor bsnyen pa ni //
NG0249:1098: om ni ye shes lnga ste khrag 'thung yab yum mo //
NG0249:1099: hu lu gong ma gau ri khro mo brgyad /
NG0249:1100: hu lu 'og ma sing ha phra men brgyad /
NG0249:1101: phat ni sgo ba chen po bzhi /
NG0249:1102: e a ra li ni dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NG0249:1104: dzahni yang sprul sum sprul don /
NG0249:1105: de la bsnyen pa dbul zhing 'gro ba'i sgrib pa sbyong */
NG0249:1106: de yis byang chub 'bras bu thob /
NG0249:1107: dbyings kyi zhi khro gsang ba'i sgrub pa'o //
NG0249:1108: om ni ye shes lnga ldan pad+ma he ru ka / hu lu gong ma drab mo dang */
NG0249:1110: hu lu 'og ma sder mo can dang gshog pa can no //
NG0249:1111: phat ni kham rgya mo drug / e dang a ni long ba ste //
NG0249:1112: ra dang li ni dmus long ngo *//
NG0249:1113: hum ni mgo brtsegs khro bo bzhi //
NG0249:1114: hrihni spyang gi za byed brgyad //
NG0249:1115: dzahni khyi brgyad rngam pa'i tshogs //
NG0249:1116: de ltar dbang gi bsnyen pa'o //
NG0249:1117: de ltar dbang gi sngags chen po //
NG0249:1118: gsung mchog 'grub ste 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob //
NG0249:1119: rta mchog rol pa'i tan tra las /
NG0249:1120: yi ge 'bru yi nges pa dang */
NG0249:1121: sgrub pa'i le'u ste bcu bzhi pa'o ///
NG0249:1122: / de nas dbang gi rgyal po de la bdud @#//
NG0249:1123: dang klu dang lang ka la sogs pas /
NG0249:1124: gdug pa'i mtshon cha'i char dbab pa'i tshe /
NG0249:1125: dbang gi rgyal po mi g.yo ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs pas /
NG0249:1126: gdug pa'i mtshon cha rnams me tog dang lha mor gyur to //
NG0249:1127: gdug pa thams cad gtan brlag zhi ste /
NG0249:1128: dgyes pas mi g.yo ba rnam pa bcu drug byung ste /
NG0249:1129: dbang chen gyi dbu'i thog tu /
NG0249:1130: rigs lnga'i rgyal ba re la /
NG0249:1131: lha mo bzhi bzhis bskor te /
NG0249:1132: tshom bu lnga'i dkyil 'khor du shar ba'o //
NG0249:1134: sgrub pa ma lus don tshang ba'o //
NG0249:1135: rta mchog rol pa'i tan tra las /
NG0249:1136: mi g.yo ba'i ngang las lha mo dang rigs sgrub
NG0249:1137: pa'i le'u ste bco lnga pa'o // // de nas
NG0249:1140: ma chags pa'i mchod pas mchod nas /
NG0249:1141: dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsol cig / bdag cag
NG0249:1142: rnams la gzhan gyis mi mthong ba'i dbang zhig bskur
NG0249:1143: / gsang ba'i ming zhig gdags su gsol /
NG0249:1144: e ma ra ga ra sid+d+hi nag tsan tra sa ma ya /
NG0249:1148: pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug chen pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0249:1151: ma bral ba na ma ra bya'o //
NG0249:1152: 'du 'bral med na bdag gi gzungs mar bya'o //
NG0249:1153: snying nye na bu mor bya'o //
NG0249:1154: ma sring rgya mtshor bya ba'i phyir /
NG0249:1155: mi 'gyur ba'i gsang mtshan sing ha dzam b+ha la /
NG0249:1156: des khyed rnams mtshan ma'i rnam par rtog pa gzhom zhing */
NG0249:1157: khyo dang ming po bran pho dang *//
NG0249:1158: bran mo la sogs bsgral ba'i phyir //
NG0249:1159: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0249:1160: thugs rje'i gshol chen 'di thogs la //
NG0249:1161: zhing chen zhing chung 'di rlog cig / ces bka' stsal te /
NG0249:1162: pad+ma dbang gi rgyal po yis /
NG0249:1163: sngar dregs pa bsgral ba'i lhag lhog la /
NG0249:1164: pany+tsa a mr-i ta yi tshogs kyis btab //
NG0249:1165: rtag pa'i ting nge 'dzin ni bsgyur /
NG0249:1166: dam tshig gi rjes su slob ste /
NG0249:1169: kha hi thang gsum gyis bstab /
NG0249:1170: le thang gsum gyis sbyangs nas /
NG0249:1172: dbang phyug ma rnams kyis gsol pa /
NG0249:1173: gar gyi dbang phyug ngo mtshar che'o //
NG0249:1174: dri phun sum tshogs pa gda' na ye shes kyi dri lags sam /
NG0249:1175: ro phun sum tshogs pa gda' na /
NG0249:1177: sgra phun sum tshogs pa gda' na /
NG0249:1178: ye shes kyi sgra lags sam /
NG0249:1179: bdag cag rnams ni sngon las kyang mthu skyes pa snyam bgyid do //
NG0249:1180: bdag cag rnams ni sngon pas kyang rdzu 'phrul skyes pa snyam bgyid do //
NG0249:1181: rig pa skyes pa snyam bgyid do //
NG0249:1182: tshor ba skyes pa snyam bgyid do //
NG0249:1183: dug sman du gyur pa lags sam /
NG0249:1184: zas bdud rtsir gyur pa lags sam /
NG0249:1185: rdzas dag pa'i nus mthu lags sam /
NG0249:1186: ji ltar bsams pa bzhin du 'grub bam snyam mo //
NG0249:1187: zhes zhus pas dbang gi rgyal po bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NG0249:1189: dang sring mo khyed rnams kyis //
NG0249:1190: dga' ba snyam du blangs so //
NG0249:1191: byang chub don du gnyer ba yis //
NG0249:1192: zhing bcu bsgral ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NG0249:1193: rtag tu smon du gyur par nges so //
NG0249:1194: zas bdud rtsir gyur pa nges so //
NG0249:1195: de'i byin rlabs kyis nga'i zhal mthong ba dang */
NG0249:1196: rta'i dbyangs thos pa yin no //
NG0249:1197: nga'i zhal mthong ba dang rta'i dbyangs thos pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NG0249:1198: yab yum thabs dang shes rab kyis sgrib pa sbyangs nas /
NG0249:1199: sgyu lus kyi 'gyur shes kyi thogs pa med pa'i dbang thob po //
NG0249:1200: de nas sing ha dzam b+ha la bi sa mi te zhes brjod pas /
NG0249:1201: skad cig gis lus gdos pa can bor nas /
NG0249:1202: gser gyi seng ge spyan gsum pa /
NG0249:1204: rdo rje'i gshog pas brgyan pa /
NG0249:1205: seng ge'i mgul pa na byu ru'i a long dmar
NG0249:1206: po re la yi ge b+h+yo dmar po re kha
NG0249:1208: de ni dbang chen gyi zhabs kyi khri'i mthongs bzhir /
NG0249:1211: mjug bskor nang du bsnol te bzhag nas /
NG0249:1212: b+h+yo zlog dang las mkhan du bskos so //
NG0249:1213: rta mchog rol pa'i tan tra las /
NG0249:1214: las kyi dbang phyug ma dam la btags shing gdan
NG0249:1215: du bting ba'i le'u ste bcu drug pa'o // //
NG0249:1216: de nas bcom ldan 'das dbang gi rgyal po la
NG0249:1217: / las kyi pad+ma sems dpas 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:1218: kye ma bcom ldan gar gyi bdag / bskul bskyod phyag rgya der bshad de //
NG0249:1219: ye shes lha tshogs 'di rnams la //
NG0249:1220: dgyes pa bskyed na gang gis bskyed //
NG0249:1221: gnad nas bskul na ji ltar lags //
NG0249:1222: dbang gi rgyal pos bshad du gsol //
NG0249:1224: bcom ldan 'das dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0249:1225: las kyi sems dpa' nyon cig / bstod dang mchod pa'i las ni 'di lta ste //
NG0249:1226: zla gam bsil ba'i dur khrod nas //
NG0249:1227: dbang gi rgyal po gar gyi bdag / rtogs pa'i ye shes dbu lnga 'bar //
NG0249:1228: dri med zhal gdangs ye shes 'od /
NG0249:1229: sku lus dmar po zhabs ni srid gsum sgrol //
NG0249:1230: ye shes rgyu yi don dang ldan //
NG0249:1232: rgyal ba'i yum chen thugs kar spras //
NG0249:1233: dri med ma chags pad+ma'i spyan //
NG0249:1234: na bza' gsum ni brjid du che //
NG0249:1235: thugs rje ye shes gshog pa 'bar //
NG0249:1237: dbang gi rgyal po khyod la bstod //
NG0249:1238: srid gsum ma lus bsgral ba'i phyir //
NG0249:1239: dpal gyi khyi brgyad las la khye //
NG0249:1240: zas su gtsang sme med par za //
NG0249:1241: de phyir mang sa sha chen zhim //
NG0249:1242: skom du kha mngar med par 'thung *//
NG0249:1243: de phyir khrag dang dri chus ngoms //
NG0249:1244: bang ni ngal dub med par rgyug / de phyir gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor skyong *//
NG0249:1245: shar gyi phyogs nas rgyug pa'i khyi //
NG0249:1248: lho yi phyogs nas rgyug pa'i khyi //
NG0249:1249: glog dmar ljibs shing gshin rje gnon //
NG0249:1250: gshin rje'i rgyal mo sha za ma //
NG0249:1255: byang gi phyogs nas rgyug pa'i khyi //
NG0249:1256: gnod sbyin sgal tshigs dra ba 'joms //
NG0249:1257: gnod sbyin stong gi snying 'byin mo //
NG0249:1258: shar lho mtshams nas rgyug pa'i khyi /
NG0249:1259: drang srong me lha dpung sgron ma //
NG0249:1260: me lha stong gi snying 'byin ma //
NG0249:1261: lho nub mtshams nas rgyug pa'i khyi //
NG0249:1262: srin po'i thod rus zas su za //
NG0249:1263: srin po'i khrag 'thung dbang mo che //
NG0249:1264: nub byang mtshams nas rgyug pa'i khyi //
NG0249:1265: rlung lha sngon mo'i ba dan gcod //
NG0249:1266: rlung lha stong gi snying 'byin mo //
NG0249:1267: byang shar mtshams nas rgyug pa'i khyi //
NG0249:1268: nyi zla gza' skar kha lang ka / dbang ldan stong gi snying 'byin po //
NG0249:1269: khyi yi brtul zhugs chen po ste //
NG0249:1270: kun kyang mi bzad ci 'dra na //
NG0249:1272: phra men thod rus khra la la //
NG0249:1273: ku ku+u ra tsa'i dus la bab //
NG0249:1274: bya yi brtul zhugs chen po ste //
NG0249:1275: rdo rje'i gshog pa gdengs pa yis //
NG0249:1276: khams gsum ma lus zil gyis gnon //
NG0249:1277: rdo rje'i sder mo bcum pa yis //
NG0249:1278: srid gsum ma lus zas su za //
NG0249:1279: gzan gyi mchog ste klu rnams za //
NG0249:1280: de phyir khyung chen gzan la rol //
NG0249:1281: rgyud drug cig car khyur mid byed //
NG0249:1282: gnam du ston pa'i byin rlabs las //
NG0249:1283: dkar mo'i tshogs dang ser mo'i tshogs //
NG0249:1284: sngon mo'i tshogs dang dmar mo'i tshogs //
NG0249:1285: ljang gu la sogs sna tshogs pa //
NG0249:1286: ser sprin bzhin du 'khrigs par byed //
NG0249:1287: la la 'jol zhing la la lding *//
NG0249:1288: la la 'bab cing la la rol //
NG0249:1289: sha chen tshogs la gshegs su gsol //
NG0249:1290: ka tag sha kwa tag sha a mu ka dza /
NG0249:1291: phag gi brtul zhugs chen po yis //
NG0249:1292: gti mug 'joms pa'i dbang phyug ma //
NG0249:1293: blang dor med pa'i mnyam pa la //
NG0249:1294: phyogs bcu stong khams nga yi khron //
NG0249:1295: khron du ma gyur gang yang med //
NG0249:1296: srid pa'i khron brko thabs re mkhas //
NG0249:1297: de mkhas thabs kyi rgyal po ste //
NG0249:1298: tshems ni 'bar ba'i rang bzhin la //
NG0249:1299: zhal ni phag rgod mche ba sbrul //
NG0249:1300: shangs ni ngan song khron pa brko //
NG0249:1301: skad ni grul bum tshogs la sgrog / skye shi rtsad nas gcad pa'i phyir //
NG0249:1302: gdug pa ma lus gzhom par bya'o //
NG0249:1303: zas ni sra snyi med par za //
NG0249:1304: tshems ni sra snyi med par 'joms //
NG0249:1305: dpa' bar byin gyis brlab pa'i phyir //
NG0249:1306: sbas pa'i tshogs kyang gzhom par bya'o //
NG0249:1307: dmyal tshogs me dpung gsad pa'i phyir //
NG0249:1308: snang srid ma lus za bar bya //
NG0249:1309: gti mug gnas su sbyang ba'i phyir //
NG0249:1310: hum dang phat kyi stang sta /
NG0249:1317: zhes gdug pa'i nga ro bsgrags so //
NG0249:1318: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:1319: bstod pa dang las la bskol ba'i le'u ste bcu
NG0249:1320: bdun pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das dbang
NG0249:1322: las kyi sems dpas yang gsol pa /
NG0249:1323: kye ma dbang gi rgyal po las kyi bdag / dbang gi lha @#//
NG0249:1325: spyan drangs pa ni ji ltar lags //
NG0249:1326: gar gyi bdag pos bshad du gsol //
NG0249:1328: dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0249:1329: nyon cig las kyi sems dpa' che //
NG0249:1330: spyan drangs pa yi las dag ni //
NG0249:1331: se gol tsam gyis snyan gsan dbab //
NG0249:1332: dbyings nas spyan drangs 'di ltar gsungs //
NG0249:1333: skye med chos kyi pho brang nas //
NG0249:1335: zla gam dmar po'i gzhal yas nas //
NG0249:1336: bcom ldan dbang chen he ru gshegs su gsol //
NG0249:1337: gnyis med ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0249:1338: gzi ldan pad+ma yab yum gshegs su gsol //
NG0249:1339: ye shes dgu yi ngang las skur bzhengs pa //
NG0249:1340: dkyil 'khor dgu yi lha tshogs gshegs su gsol //
NG0249:1341: tshad med bzhi las khro mo'i skur bstan bzhi //
NG0249:1342: sgo ba g.yog 'khor bcas pa gshegs su gsol //
NG0249:1343: tshom bu lnga dang ye shes 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0249:1344: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NG0249:1345: zla gam zhal sprod dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0249:1346: rta mgrin dbang gi dkyil 'khor ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NG0249:1347: zla gam dgu brtsegs dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0249:1348: hum mdzad chen po 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NG0249:1350: khams gsum rnam rgyal yab yum gshegs su gsol //
NG0249:1351: gru bzhi gdengs pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0249:1352: ngan song sbyong ba'i lha rnams gshegs su gsol //
NG0249:1353: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad 'bar ba'i gzhal yas nas //
NG0249:1354: 'gro ba 'dul ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NG0249:1356: ye shes sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NG0249:1357: gnyis med rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0249:1358: lhun gyis grub pa'i tshogs bcas gshegs su gsol //
NG0249:1359: 'bar ba'i le'u tshe dgu yi dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0249:1360: dur khrod chen po'i lha tshogs gshegs su gsol //
NG0249:1362: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las //
NG0249:1363: spyan drangs pa'i le'u ste bco brgyad pa'o //  // dkyil 'khor dgu yi gzhal yas nas //
NG0249:1364: yi ge dgu dang phyag rgya dgu //
NG0249:1365: dbyings nas don du spyan drangs te //
NG0249:1366: gdan khri rnams la bzhugs su gsol //
NG0249:1367: mdzes shing spras pa'i gdan khri la //
NG0249:1368: ye shes lha tshogs bzhugs su gsol //
NG0249:1369: sha khrag rlon pa'i gdan khri ni //
NG0249:1370: ma dad bsgral ba'i gdan khri la //
NG0249:1371: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs bcas bzhugs su gsol //
NG0249:1372: lhag thed lhag lhog ga go la //
NG0249:1373: lhag sdud 'khor bcas bzhugs su gsol //
NG0249:1374: i ta pa hu lus ma ya tish+tha lhan /
NG0249:1376: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:1377: dbang gi lha rnams bzhugs su gsol ba'i le'u ste
NG0249:1378: bcu dgu pa'o // // de nas yang dbang gi
NG0249:1379: rgyal po la / pad+ma las kyi sems dpas @#//
NG0249:1381: dbang gi lha tshogs 'di rnams la //
NG0249:1382: phyag 'tshal ba ni ci ltar lags //
NG0249:1383: gar gyi dbang phyug chen pos bshad du gsol //
NG0249:1384: skye med chos dbyings ngang las skur bzhengs te //
NG0249:1385: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus las mi 'da' bar //
NG0249:1386: nyon mongs 'joms pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0249:1387: khams gsum bsgral kyang nyes pa'i skyon ma gos //
NG0249:1388: 'dam skyes pad+ma lta bur sku 'khrungs pas //
NG0249:1389: skyon gyis ma gos pad+ma ra ga'i mdog / rgyal bas bsngags pa'i yum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0249:1390: chos sku zhi ba'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang *//
NG0249:1391: sprul sku rigs kyi dkyil 'khor lhar bzhugs pa //
NG0249:1392: dbyings kyi lha tshogs kun la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0249:1393: pha rol phyin rdzogs 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NG0249:1394: ye shes ma g.yos chos mchog ngang la gnas //
NG0249:1395: dkyil 'khor dgu yi lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0249:1396: gdug pa 'dul phyir sprul pa'i tshogs //
NG0249:1397: las mdzad chen po kun la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0249:1399: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:1400: dbang gi lha la phyag 'tshal ba'i le'u ste nyi
NG0249:1401: shu pa'o // // de nas las kyi sems dpa'
NG0249:1402: des // gar gyi dbang phyug chen po la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:1403: bcom ldan gsang ba gar gyi bdag / e ma
NG0249:1404: ngo mtshar thugs rje'i bdag / mchod pa chen po'i
NG0249:1407: dbang gi rgyal pos bkal stsal pa /
NG0249:1408: pad+ma las kyi sems dpa' khyod nyon cig / mchod pa chen po brgyad yod de //
NG0249:1409: ma dad chen po bsgral ba ni //
NG0249:1410: phyag rgya chen pos sgrol ba'o //
NG0249:1411: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad phyag rgyas dgyes pa bskyed pa'o //
NG0249:1412: dang por phyi nang phyag rgya chen pos mchod do //
NG0249:1413: de nas chos thams cad mnyam pa chen po yin pas /
NG0249:1414: mnyam pa'i ngang las kun tu bzang pos mchod //
NG0249:1415: bde bar gshegs pa khro rgyal gtso //
NG0249:1416: rgyal ba rgya mtsho ye shes kyi //
NG0249:1417: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
NG0249:1418: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NG0249:1419: na mahsarba ta tha ga ta b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NG0249:1420: khe b+h+yahsarba tha kham ud ga te s+pha na i
NG0249:1421: mam ga ga na kham swa ha /
NG0249:1422: las kyi sems dpa' nyon cig / chos thams cad
NG0249:1423: ni phyi'i yul dang nang gis sems su 'dus so
NG0249:1425: om pa na pe ma pe nu su ra ti
NG0249:1426: pa ra mu sarba ta tha ga ta si ti
NG0249:1427: hu / sa ma yo ta muh /
NG0249:1434: las kyi sems dpa' nyon cig / ma dad pa
NG0249:1435: chen po bsgral ba'i phung po 'di dag bdud rtsir
NG0249:1436: byin gyis brlabs te rol lo //
NG0249:1439: rtsa ba sems rtsa chen po brgyad la rgyu bas rtsa ba brgyad do //
NG0249:1441: dbang po ni ra sa ya na la sogs pa'o //
NG0249:1442: de rnams ni bdud rtsi chen po'o //
NG0249:1443: des ni lha rnams la mchod pa'o //
NG0249:1444: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag / rtsa ba @#//
NG0249:1446: sangs rgyas thams cad mchod pa'o //
NG0249:1447: sha gti mug / zhe sdang rus /
NG0249:1448: 'dod chags khrag / dug gsum ma spangs dag pa'i 'dod yon gtor ma'o //
NG0249:1449: rlan gyis bsdus pa'i khrag dang mam sa dang */
NG0249:1450: ma dad pa'i khrag rnams sbyangs pa rak+tar rol ba'o //
NG0249:1451: gnyis med sbyor ba'i byang chub sems ni gsang bar mchod pa'o //
NG0249:1452: de dag thams cad bsdus te phul ba na sgra dang bcas pa ni stod tshig mchod pa'o //
NG0249:1453: de dag thams cad gnyis su med par mchod pa ni /
NG0249:1455: de ltar sangs rgyas mchod na dngos grub thob //
NG0249:1457: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:1458: mchod pa'i rim par bstan pa'i le'u ste nyer gcig pa'o ///
NG0249:1459: / de nas yang las kyi sems dpas /
NG0249:1460: gar gyi dbang phyug la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:1461: bcom ldan gsang ba gar gyi bdag / dbang gi lha tshogs thams cad la //
NG0249:1462: de ltar mchod cing bstod pa na //
NG0249:1463: dngos grub las ni ji ltar 'thob //
NG0249:1465: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa //
NG0249:1466: pad+ma las kyi sems dpa' nyon //
NG0249:1467: de ltar mchod cing bstod pa na //
NG0249:1468: dngos grub chen po de lta bu //
NG0249:1469: sku dang gsung dang thugs dang ni //
NG0249:1470: yon tan phrin las dngos grub thob //
NG0249:1471: gzhan yang 'dod pa phun sum tshogs //
NG0249:1472: thams cad byang chub chen po yi //
NG0249:1474: sbyangs kyin zos na sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub 'thob //
NG0249:1475: 'phros pas bcud bsdus slar bsdus dbyings su thim //
NG0249:1476: thugs kar thim nas sku yi dbyig / gsung mchog gsung gi dngos grub thob //
NG0249:1477: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:1478: dngos grub bstan pa'i le'u ste nyer gnyis pa'o //
NG0249:1479: // de nas yang pad+ma las kyi sems dpa' des
NG0249:1480: // pad+ma gar gyi bdag po la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:1481: e ma'o bde gshegs bdud rtsi mchog gi bdag /
NG0249:1482: dregs pa ma dad nyon mongs lnga la zhen pa
NG0249:1483: zag dang bcas // longs spyod rnam pa lnga po zag med bdud rtsir rol pa dang *//
NG0249:1484: thugs rje yongs su mdzad pa yis //
NG0249:1485: sman dang 'bru rnams thams cad kun //
NG0249:1486: rtsa ba yan lag bcas pa kun //
NG0249:1487: sangs rgyas sems can kun gyi gsos su mdzad pa'i tshe //
NG0249:1488: rjes su 'jug pa ji ltar bgyi //
NG0249:1489: bdud rtsi mchog la bdag mnyan 'tshal //
NG0249:1491: bdud rtsi mchog gis bka' stsal pa //
NG0249:1492: e ma'o las kyi sems dpa' che //
NG0249:1493: phyi rabs rnal 'byor don gyi phyir //
NG0249:1494: bdud rtsi'i don zhus ya mtshan che'o //
NG0249:1495: bdud rtsi'i don 'di ngas bshad kyis /
NG0249:1496: las kyi sems dpa' yid la zung *//
NG0249:1497: nyon mongs pa yi bdud nyid la //
NG0249:1498: thugs rje chen po'i rtsi btang nas //
NG0249:1499: khyab pa'i ye shes chen po yi //
NG0249:1500: dbyings su dkyil 'khor bdud rtsi'i don //
NG0249:1501: kun rdzob rtags su bsgrub bya na //
NG0249:1502: kun rdzob kyis ni bsgrub pa de //
NG0249:1504: 'khor yug / ye nas ma bcos rang bzhin snod //
NG0249:1505: de yi nang du blugs pa'i sman //
NG0249:1506: bdud rtsi rtsa ba lo ma rnams //
NG0249:1507: dbyer med ngang du bsogs par bya //
NG0249:1508: de la nges pa'i bsam pa yis //
NG0249:1509: nges pa nyid du bsgrub par bya'o //
NG0249:1510: mi phyed rgyur ldan slob dpon gyis //
NG0249:1511: thams cad ma lus don bya'i phyir //
NG0249:1512: bdud rtsi dam pa bsgrub par bya'o //
NG0249:1513: rin chen ri dang sman ljongs yul //
NG0249:1514: rtsi sman 'khrungs pa'i sa phyogs sam //
NG0249:1515: nags tshal me tog rgyas par bsgrub //
NG0249:1516: 'khor du bya ba'i rim pa yang *//
NG0249:1517: skyon drug rnam par spangs pa yi //
NG0249:1518: nyi shu'am bcu 'am yang na lnga //
NG0249:1519: khrims dang sdom pas bcings pa min //
NG0249:1520: dang por ra ba'i tshes brgyad la //
NG0249:1521: der ni brtsams pa'i dus yin no //
NG0249:1522: rtags kyi don nyid mthong ba'am //
NG0249:1523: dus ni bcu drug nyid la'o //
NG0249:1524: yo byad ma lus ldan gyur na //
NG0249:1526: ma tshogs pa ni 'grub thag ring *//
NG0249:1527: de bas yo byad ldan par bya //
NG0249:1528: bkra shis mtshan ldan b+han d+ha lnga //
NG0249:1529: dam rdzas lnga dang sha lnga dang *//
NG0249:1530: phyi nang gsang ba'i rtsa brgyad sogs //
NG0249:1531: dang por ra sa ya na kun //
NG0249:1532: so so'i rigs dang sde phye la //
NG0249:1533: sman gyi srung ma bos mchod bstim //
NG0249:1534: dam rdzas rnams kyi rtog pa gzhom //
NG0249:1535: rigs kyi kha dog dar gyis dgab //
NG0249:1536: mtshan ldan bkra shis gzungs thag gdags //
NG0249:1537: de ni bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NG0249:1538: bsgrub pa'i zhag grangs ci tsam par //
NG0249:1539: bar chad bgegs rnams bsal ba'i phyir //
NG0249:1540: phyi nang gsang ba'i rgyu 'drul bsdams //
NG0249:1542: nyon mongs bag chags sbyang ba'i phyir //
NG0249:1543: 'bum lnga'i bshags pa bya ba ste //
NG0249:1544: ngan song sbyong ba'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NG0249:1545: khrol bu la ni 'khor lo ste //
NG0249:1546: gdung bzhi ka ba brgyad btang ba'i //
NG0249:1547: bzhi brgyad sgo dang bcas pa'o //
NG0249:1548: phye ma'i dus na brgyad cha bzhi //
NG0249:1549: ka ba 'khor lo pad+ma rin chen sgo //
NG0249:1550: gong bu'i dus na zla gam kha sprod sgo bzhir bcas //
NG0249:1551: gzugs brnyan 'gro ba 'dul ba'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NG0249:1552: rigs brgyas sbyang dang rigs lnga'am //
NG0249:1553: gsang chen rigs gcig bsnyen pa yis //
NG0249:1554: de ni khrol bu sbyang ba ste //
NG0249:1555: ye shes lnga yi 'phro 'dus phye ma sbyang *//
NG0249:1556: dgu pa'i sngags ni gong bu la'o //
NG0249:1557: om ahhum sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0249:1559: gtan pa lnga la mkha' lnga dbyings //
NG0249:1560: rdung byed lnga la gsang ba'i mtshan bris la //
NG0249:1561: btsag pa'i 'tshags snod yab yum ste //
NG0249:1562: srin mtheb thabs dang shes rab po //
NG0249:1563: btag btsag bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NG0249:1564: zla gam sgo shar bltas pa la //
NG0249:1566: rta mgrin dbang gi dkyil 'khor ro //
NG0249:1567: lta ba bla med gdeng du blta //
NG0249:1568: spyod pa bla med gdeng du spyad //
NG0249:1569: dam tshig bsrung ba bla med gdeng *//
NG0249:1570: phrin las bla med gdeng du bshad //
NG0249:1573: bdud rtsi chen po bum pa yis //
NG0249:1574: phyi dang nang dang gsang ba'i dbang *//
NG0249:1575: 'dod pa de la rab sbyin pa //
NG0249:1576: dbang chen bla na med pa'i gdeng *//
NG0249:1577: dngos grub bla na med pa'i gdeng *//
NG0249:1578: bla na med pa'i gdeng brgyad kyis //
NG0249:1579: bdud rtsi dam pa mchog bsgrubs pas //
NG0249:1580: sangs rgyas mchod cing rang zos na //
NG0249:1581: bdud rtsi dam pa bsgrub pa 'grub //
NG0249:1582: dngos grub khyad par can yang thob //
NG0249:1583: dam rdzas sman sna re re yang *//
NG0249:1584: yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab cing *//
NG0249:1585: byin brlabs mthu byin de bzhin no //
NG0249:1586: de yi nus mthus dpag las 'das //
NG0249:1588: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:1589: bdud rtsi chen po bsgrub pa'i le'u ste nyer gsum
NG0249:1590: pa'o // // de nas yang pad+ma las kyi sems
NG0249:1591: dpa' des / pad+ma gar gyi bdag po la /
NG0249:1592: ma chags pa'i mchod pas mchod nas 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:1593: kye ma sangs rgyas dbang gi mchog / ma dad chen po bsgral ba'i tshe //
NG0249:1594: thams cad yi ge a 'tsher bsdus //
NG0249:1595: tshe'u+u ba tshe gang mdzad pa'i tshe //
NG0249:1596: rjes su 'jug pas ji ltar bgyi //
NG0249:1597: tshe dpag med pa bdag nyan 'tshal //
NG0249:1599: tshe yi bdag pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0249:1600: e ma'o las kyi sems dpa' che //
NG0249:1601: phyi rabs rnal 'byor don gyi phyir //
NG0249:1602: tshe mchog las zhus ya mtshan che'o //
NG0249:1603: tshe yi las 'di bshad kyis sems dpas zung *//
NG0249:1604: 'gro drug tshe dang shes pa kun //
NG0249:1605: nyon mongs bdud kyis glags btsal nas //
NG0249:1606: tshe nyams pa dang tshe 'thor dang *//
NG0249:1607: tshe bri ba dang tshe yar rnams //
NG0249:1608: nr-i tshe la sogs 'thor ba na //
NG0249:1609: drug gi gnas nas bkug nas su //
NG0249:1610: khro bo 'chol pa'i sprul pas kun bkang ste //
NG0249:1611: tshe dpag med ni zhi tshogs la //
NG0249:1612: de la bsnyen cing bsgrub slad phyag rgya'o //
NG0249:1613: zhi ba'i las kyis ma 'grub na //
NG0249:1614: tshe dpag med kyang khro bo ste //
NG0249:1615: lha tshogs ma lus khro bor gsal //
NG0249:1616: spros zhing khro bos kun bkang ste //
NG0249:1617: thams cad ma lus spros nas su //
NG0249:1618: khro bo'i sprul pa ma lus pas //
NG0249:1619: gzhom dang gtub cing bcom nas su //
NG0249:1620: thams cad bsgral bcom tshe yi rang bzhin bkug / bum pa'i tshe la bstim pa'o //
NG0249:1621: yab yum sbyor ba'i byang chub sems //
NG0249:1622: yab kyi byang chub sems kyi tshe 'di dkar la dngas //
NG0249:1623: yum gyi tshe ni dmar la dngas //
NG0249:1624: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i tshe ni snum la 'dril //
NG0249:1625: spro bsdu 'od kyi rang bzhin las //
NG0249:1626: thams cad tshe bkug de la bstim //
NG0249:1629: ham b+h+rum hrihb+h+rum yam b+h+rum tshe b+h+rum /
NG0249:1630: om b+h+rum badzra a yu she hum a /
NG0249:1631: rtsa ba'i lha re'i sngags gzhug tu //
NG0249:1632: gdags shing de la bzlas pa'o //
NG0249:1633: a yu ra gnya' na shi bi du gnya' na a ba lo ki ti sa man ta /
NG0249:1634: s+pha ra na rasmi b+ha ba ma ha ma ni
NG0249:1635: du ru du ru hr-i da dza la ni a
NG0249:1636: b+h+rum / badzra a yu she hum a /
NG0249:1637: dung dung badzra dung ya ra ga ho /
NG0249:1639: skyed pa dang ni dral ba dang *//
NG0249:1642: bstim pa dang ni sba ba'o //
NG0249:1643: phyag rgya dang ni dbang bskur ro //
NG0249:1644: man+dal mchod pa rnam lnga yis //
NG0249:1645: ting 'dzin gsal ba'i lha mos mchod //
NG0249:1646: phyogs mtshams phyogs kyi rgyal po bzhi //
NG0249:1647: bar mtshams ma tang de bsgral lo //
NG0249:1648: gsang mtshams khro bo rim pa bzhin //
NG0249:1649: brgya byin dbang la las bcol lo //
NG0249:1650: de nas man+dal rdo rje dbyings //
NG0249:1651: ga dar byi dor thig rnams bya //
NG0249:1652: tshom bu lnga la bum pa re //
NG0249:1653: yang ni mdzes pa'i dar gyis brgyan //
NG0249:1654: kha dog dmar dang ser dang ljang *//
NG0249:1655: ma nyams ras kyis mgul pa bcing *//
NG0249:1656: 'bras bu ldan pa'i ro mchog shing gis kha brgyan no //
NG0249:1657: snying po lnga dang sman lnga dang *//
NG0249:1658: 'bras bu lnga sogs tshul bzhin bsags //
NG0249:1659: der ni lha rnams bskyed bstim mchod //
NG0249:1660: gzungs thag lnga dang ldan par bya //
NG0249:1662: de nas dbang gi dkyil 'khor te //
NG0249:1663: zla gam sgo dang bcas pa ni //
NG0249:1664: bum pa dag ni dgod bzhin dang *//
NG0249:1665: ga pur srad dang ri lu dang *//
NG0249:1666: phyag rgya'i rgya dang 'phel ba dag / rgya gram bsdams pa 'phel bar gdags //
NG0249:1667: dkar dmar 'bras rgyas de bzhin te //
NG0249:1668: tshe yi las kyi sgrub pa de //
NG0249:1669: thams cad tshe yi bsgrub pa'o //
NG0249:1670: bkra shis tshe dang gzi byin che //
NG0249:1671: tshe ni bkug bstim phyag rgyas bsdams //
NG0249:1672: de ltar bsgrub na tshe chen thob //
NG0249:1674: rta mchog rol pa'i rgyud chen po las /
NG0249:1675: gzi byin sgrub pa'i le'u ste nyer bzhi pa'o //
NG0249:1676: // de nas yang bcom ldan 'das dbang gi rgyal
NG0249:1677: po la pad+ma las kyi sems dpa' des 'di skad
NG0249:1678: ces gsol to // kye ma bcom ldan dbang gi bdag / dbang mchog 'bar ba lha yi tshogs //
NG0249:1679: rjes su 'jug pas ji ltar bskang *//
NG0249:1680: dbang gi lha la bdag nyan to //
NG0249:1681: dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsol cig / ces gsol to //
NG0249:1682: dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0249:1683: las kyi sems dpa' legs par nyon la yid la zung *//
NG0249:1684: dbang gi lha rnams bskang ba na //
NG0249:1685: ma dad sems can ru tra de //
NG0249:1686: snying rje chen pos bsgral nas su //
NG0249:1687: thams cad bdud rtsir byin brlab lha rnams rol //
NG0249:1688: de yis bde gshegs thugs dam bskang *//
NG0249:1689: mam sa rak+ta keng rus gtor mar 'bul //
NG0249:1690: dug gsum gtams pas thugs dam bskang *//
NG0249:1691: de phyir rmad du byung ba'i gtor mas bskang *//
NG0249:1692: ra ga rak+ta chags pas bskang *//
NG0249:1693: thams cad gzugs dang gzugs med de yis bskang *//
NG0249:1694: de ltar bskangs pas dngos grub 'thob //
NG0249:1695: pany+tsa bdud rtsi chen pos bskang *//
NG0249:1696: rmad du byung ba'i gtor mas bskang *//
NG0249:1697: thugs rje chags pa'i rak+tas bskang *//
NG0249:1698: bya dang lug gi mdangs kyis bskang *//
NG0249:1699: thams cad bskangs pas thams cad bzlog / de phyir skong zlog chen po'o //
NG0249:1700: sems can yid dang kun gzhi yis //
NG0249:1701: dbang chen yab yum thugs dam bskang *//
NG0249:1702: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba lnga //
NG0249:1705: yid chos mi dge log pa rnams //
NG0249:1706: dbyings kyi lha dang 'gro ba 'dul bas bskang *//
NG0249:1707: 'byung ba lnga dang sde bzhi yis //
NG0249:1708: dkyil 'khor dgu yi thugs dam bskang *//
NG0249:1709: nad dang sde'u bcas pa yis //
NG0249:1710: khyi spyang tshogs kyi thugs dam bskang *//
NG0249:1711: 'di yi tshogs lhag tshogs rnams kyis //
NG0249:1712: long ba rgyab 'brel thugs dam bskang *//
NG0249:1713: 'di yi yan lag sde bzhi yis //
NG0249:1714: sgo bzhi'i khro bo'i thugs dam bskang *//
NG0249:1715: 'di yi nang khrol ma lus kyis //
NG0249:1716: 'bum phrag yangs pa'i thugs dam bskang *//
NG0249:1717: 'di'i re mig sgal tshigs 'dra yin nam nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyis //
NG0249:1718: gser gyi seng ge nyi shu rtsa brgyad thugs dam bskang *//
NG0249:1719: mtshan ma gsum dang rgyu mchog dang *//
NG0249:1720: mkha' la lding ba'i rig pa 'dis //
NG0249:1721: dbang gi lha tshogs thugs dam bskang *//
NG0249:1723: rta mchog rol pa'i rgyud las /
NG0249:1724: lha rnams thugs dam bskang pa'i le'u ste nyer lnga
NG0249:1725: pa'o // // de nas yang las kyi sems dpas
NG0249:1726: / bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:1727: kye ma bcom ldan gsang ba'i bdag / phyi rabs pa yi don slad du //
NG0249:1728: dngos grub blang ba bdag mnyan 'tshal //
NG0249:1730: dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0249:1731: phyi rabs pa yi don slad du //
NG0249:1732: dngos grub blang ba 'di ltar bshad //
NG0249:1733: gsang ba'i thabs dang shes rab la //
NG0249:1735: dngos grub thabs ni sku gsung thugs //
NG0249:1736: de dang ldan pa'i rtsal mchog des //
NG0249:1737: byin gyis brlabs shing blang bar bya //
NG0249:1738: thams cad byang chub sems su gnas //
NG0249:1739: spros shing bsdus te dbyings la thim //
NG0249:1740: om dang am dang hum gsum ni //
NG0249:1741: sku gsung thugs su bsdus nas ni //
NG0249:1742: de dang ldan par blang byas na //
NG0249:1743: dngos grub thams cad des thob gsungs //
NG0249:1744: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:1745: dngos grub blang ba'i le'u ste nyer drug pa'o //
NG0249:1746: // de nas yang pad+ma las kyi sems dpa' des
NG0249:1747: / dbang gi rgyal po la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:1748: kye ma gsang mchog gsang ba'i bdag / gsang ba dbang gi lha tshogs la //
NG0249:1749: phrin las bcol ba bdag nyan 'tshal //
NG0249:1751: dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0249:1752: pad+ma las kyi sems dpa' nyon //
NG0249:1753: gsang ba dbang gi lha rnams la //
NG0249:1754: phrin las bcol ba 'di skad gsungs //
NG0249:1755: zla gam dbang gi dkyil 'khor du //
NG0249:1756: thabs dang shes rab ldan byas te //
NG0249:1757: sbyor ba'i phrin las lha rnams spro //
NG0249:1758: spros shing bkug ste thams cad dbang du sdud //
NG0249:1759: dbang du ma 'dus gang yang med //
NG0249:1760: dbang gi rdzas kyis mchod cing phrin las bcol //
NG0249:1761: ma dad pa las dur khrod byung *//
NG0249:1762: dur khrod las ni dbang gi dkyil 'khor byas //
NG0249:1763: dbang gi lha la phyag 'tshal nas //
NG0249:1764: mchod cing bstod la phrin las bcol //
NG0249:1765: dmigs pa ma lus dbang du sdud //
NG0249:1768: zhi ba'i lha ni yab yum bcas //
NG0249:1769: mchod bstod phrin las bcol te las bya'o //
NG0249:1770: gru bzhi gdengs pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0249:1771: rgyas pa'i rdzas dang lha rnams bzhugs //
NG0249:1772: mchod bstod phrin las bcol ba'o //
NG0249:1773: gru gsum gdengs pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NG0249:1774: drag po'i lha la de bzhin no //
NG0249:1777: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:1778: phrin las bcol ba'i le'u ste nyer bdun pa'o //  // de nas yang pad+ma las kyi sems dpas /
NG0249:1779: pad+ma gar gyi bdag po la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:1780: kye ma pad+ma gar dbang lha //
NG0249:1781: sems can las kyi dbang song na //
NG0249:1782: phyi rabs pa yi don phyir du //
NG0249:1783: drag po sgrol ba bdag nyan 'tshal //
NG0249:1785: dbang mchog rgyal pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0249:1786: pad+ma las kyi sems dpa' nyon //
NG0249:1787: gdug pa bsgral ba'i las bstan pa //
NG0249:1788: ma dad pa la rgyu gcig ste //
NG0249:1789: ma dad pa dang tshul bstun to //
NG0249:1790: phyi ni gru bzhi gdengs pa la //
NG0249:1791: nang ni zla gam 'bar ba bris //
NG0249:1792: zla gam nang du dmigs pa ste //
NG0249:1793: yan lag gsang gnas bcas par bri //
NG0249:1794: dbang gi sngags kyis spyi nas gnan //
NG0249:1795: khyi spyang sngags ni yan lag la //
NG0249:1796: mkha' 'khor sngags ni g.yas g.yon bskor //
NG0249:1797: dpral bar rus la snying gar ming *//
NG0249:1798: ma ra ya ni 'doms su ste //
NG0249:1799: sgo bzhir khro bo bzhi'i sngags dgod //
NG0249:1800: de ltar bcas shing las bya ste //
NG0249:1801: phyogs bzhir brtul zhugs bzhi yi sngags //
NG0249:1802: phyi nas che ba'i nga rgyal bskul //
NG0249:1803: phyogs bzhir brtul zhugs chen por brdung *//
NG0249:1804: gdug pa'i mtshon cha'i char yang dbab //
NG0249:1805: drag sngags bdun ni snying gar brdung *//
NG0249:1806: phur pa bla dang bcas pas gdab //
NG0249:1807: gdug pa'i mtshon dang tho ba lcags kyu dang *//
NG0249:1808: gu gul dang ni nyung dkar dang *//
NG0249:1809: ma bdun dang ni sme rdzas bdug pas brdeg /
NG0249:1810: sgrol sngags rnams ni spungs la brdeg / pho nya
NG0249:1812: dum bur bsgral te lha la bstab //
NG0249:1813: lhag ma la ni bro brdung ngo *//
NG0249:1814: de yis drag po'i las 'grub bo //
NG0249:1816: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:1817: drag pos sgrol ba'i las bstan pa'i le'u ste nyer
NG0249:1818: brgyad pa'o // // de nas yang pad+ma las kyi
NG0249:1819: sems dpas dbang gi rgyal po la 'di skad ces
NG0249:1820: gsol to // kye ma dbang mchog dbang gi bdag / 'gro ba phyi rabs don slad du //
NG0249:1821: bzlog pa'i las ni bdag nyan 'tshal //
NG0249:1823: dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0249:1824: pad+ma las kyi sems dpa' nyon cig / ye shes lha dang 'jig rten lha rnams ni //
NG0249:1825: bzlog cing rbad nas las byas na //
NG0249:1827: zla gam gru gsum man+dal bya //
NG0249:1828: gong bzhin mchod pa bstab pa ste //
NG0249:1829: gdeng brgyad mi phyed ldan pa yis //
NG0249:1830: tsa ra rog po'i mkhal dkar ram //
NG0249:1831: dmar kham spu mdog khug pa yis //
NG0249:1834: dmigs pa dgug gzhug de la bya //
NG0249:1835: dang po dkyil 'khor rtsar drangs la //
NG0249:1836: byin gyis brlabs shing ging dbang bskur //
NG0249:1837: sems can chen po de la ni //
NG0249:1838: 'bru lnga'i sa bon gsal ba la //
NG0249:1839: ngan song nas 'don so so'i rtsar //
NG0249:1840: 'bru lnga'i yi ge dgod par bya //
NG0249:1841: spyan dbye dkyil 'khor bstan par bya //
NG0249:1842: de nas phung po ma bshig par la ni //
NG0249:1843: lha rnams bskang zhing dmigs rnams bskyed pa'o //
NG0249:1844: ti ra'i ting nge 'dzin chen po yis //
NG0249:1845: phung po de ni bslang bar bya //
NG0249:1846: drag sngags sgrol sngags de yi ni //
NG0249:1847: phung po srung byed de dang phral //
NG0249:1848: khro bo'i stangs stabs chen po dang *//
NG0249:1849: phra men 'jol tshul chen po dang *//
NG0249:1850: ma mo'i gar thabs dag gis zung *//
NG0249:1851: rol pa'i brtul zhugs chen pos gzhom //
NG0249:1852: lha yi ngo bor gsal ba de //
NG0249:1853: de la phung po spros nas ni //
NG0249:1854: zla gam dbus la snying gzhag ste //
NG0249:1855: phung po lnga ni tshom bu la //
NG0249:1856: rnam shes rnams ni bskor ba'o //
NG0249:1857: de nas lha bstod mchod par bya //
NG0249:1858: lha rnams so so'i thugs dam bskang *//
NG0249:1859: srog brjes zin par sha khrag dang *//
NG0249:1860: dug dang rdzas kyi mchod pa bzlog pa'o //
NG0249:1861: de ltar bzlog na 'chi bdag gshin rje nyid kyang bzlog / ces gsungs pa la the tshom med //
NG0249:1862: stabs dang spar dang sbyar ba'o //
NG0249:1863: dbang gi dkyil 'khor dgu shes bya //
NG0249:1864: de ltar skad cig dge spyad sangs rgyas rgyu //
NG0249:1866: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:1867: bzlog pa'i le'u ste nyer dgu pa'o //  // de nas yang las kyi pad+ma sems dpa' /
NG0249:1868: pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:1869: kye ma bcom ldan dbang gi bdag / ma dad pa yi sems can de //
NG0249:1870: lus sbyang ba dang sems sbyang ba //
NG0249:1871: phyi rabs don du bshad du gsol //
NG0249:1873: dbang gi bdag pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0249:1874: las kyi sems dpa' chen po nyon cig / phyi rabs don du gnas sbyang ba //
NG0249:1875: ma dad pa yi sems can ltar //
NG0249:1876: lus sbyang ba dang sems sbyang ba //
NG0249:1877: gnyis su med par sprad cing ston //
NG0249:1878: lus sbyang ba yi rim pa ni //
NG0249:1879: rtsa bdun zhag grangs tshun chad du //
NG0249:1880: las kyi dge ba'i stongs su ste //
NG0249:1881: gnas pa zin te myur bar thon //
NG0249:1882: de nas gnas spar rgyas gdab cing *//
NG0249:1883: de yang ting 'dzin rab kyis zhugs //
NG0249:1884: de la sbyangs nas 'byongs par gsungs //
NG0249:1885: rgyas pa'i rim pa bstan pa yang *//
NG0249:1886: 'dus sbyang pa yi rim pa ni //
NG0249:1887: dang por sngags dang gtsang mas dkru //
NG0249:1888: de nas dri zhim gtsang mas byug / dbang bskur bstod dang mchod pa ste //
NG0249:1889: phung po lha la mchod par 'bul //
NG0249:1890: go bgo gnas la lha rnams dgod //
NG0249:1891: spyan drang mchod cing bstod de sbyang bar gsol ba gdab //
NG0249:1892: mi snang lha yi ngo bor thim //
NG0249:1893: rus pa sku gdung mchod rten de //
NG0249:1894: dus gsum mchod pa'i rten du bzhugs pa'o //
NG0249:1895: spyan drang rab bskyed mchod pa de bzhin bya //
NG0249:1898: dang por khrus byad blta ba bya //
NG0249:1899: de nas dbang dang lha gnyis bskyed pa'o //
NG0249:1900: de la hu lu'i 'bru yi 'phro 'dus sbyang *//
NG0249:1901: phung po lha yi gzhug gnas te //
NG0249:1902: dur khrod lnga pos mchod par 'bul //
NG0249:1903: sems ni gnyis med ngang du spar //
NG0249:1904: dug lnga ma spangs gnas su sbyang *//
NG0249:1905: sa ts+tshar phyi rabs don du sbyang *//
NG0249:1906: gnyis med ngang du mchod cing sbyang *//
NG0249:1907: dngos grub blangs shing de'i phung po 'byongs pa'o //
NG0249:1908: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:1909: lus sbyong ba'i le'u ste sum cu tham pa'o //  // de nas dbang gi rgyal pos gsungs /
NG0249:1910: las kyi sems dpa' nyon cig / sems sbyangs pa yi rim pa ni //
NG0249:1911: ma dad chen po sbyangs pa ltar //
NG0249:1912: phyi rabs don du sbyang ba ni //
NG0249:1913: lha rnams mchod cing bstod bskul nas //
NG0249:1914: de nas 'phro 'dus sems kyi ngang du gsal //
NG0249:1915: ting 'dzin chen po ldan pa des //
NG0249:1916: drug gi gnas nas bkug nas su //
NG0249:1917: snga ma'i rten la bstim par bya //
NG0249:1918: phung po bdag po bskul nas su //
NG0249:1919: sdig pa sbyang zhing lha ngo bstan //
NG0249:1920: bstim dang dbang bskur sdig pa bshags //
NG0249:1921: 'og min bla med gnas mchog na //
NG0249:1922: yab yum gnyis med phyag rgya nas //
NG0249:1923: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje che //
NG0249:1924: sbyor ba'i lhums su phat kyis 'phangs //
NG0249:1925: rdo rje dbyings kyi gral du dgod //
NG0249:1926: yi ge dpa' bo 'bru lnga yi //
NG0249:1927: dug lnga'i yi ge ma spangs bcom //
NG0249:1928: rnam shes rgyal ba'i sras su byas //
NG0249:1929: dbang bskur gzhan don gsol ba btab //
NG0249:1930: sbyang dang bstod dang sngags pa'o //
NG0249:1932: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:1933: sems sbyangs pa'i le'u ste so gcig pa'o //  // de nas yang pad+ma las kyi sems dpas /
NG0249:1934: dbang gi rgyal po la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:1935: e ma dbang mchog gsang ba'i bdag / sngon 'gro'i las ni ji ltar lags //
NG0249:1938: dbang chen gsang bas bka' stsal pa /
NG0249:1939: las kyi sems dpa' nyon cig / las kyi sngon 'gro bshad par bya //
NG0249:1940: las kyi lha ru gsol ba des //
NG0249:1941: dang po sa yi lha mor sbran //
NG0249:1942: phyag rgya lnga yi sa sbyang ngo *//
NG0249:1943: sngags dang phyag rgyas sbyang ba dang *//
NG0249:1945: g.yar ba dang ni bslang ba'o //
NG0249:1946: snang dang mi snang ngo bor brtag / mchod bstod sa rin gus par dbul //
NG0249:1947: brtag pa de ru gnas par bya //
NG0249:1948: ro lnga bsal dang yon tan bstan //
NG0249:1949: brtag pa dang ni yon tan skyon //
NG0249:1950: spang blang gnyis su shes par bya //
NG0249:1951: de ru dkyil 'khor mnga' gsol brtsig / mtha' dbus mnyam ste tshad ldan bya //
NG0249:1952: las kyi phyag rgya gsal bar bya //
NG0249:1953: chag chag rnam gsum rim par gdab //
NG0249:1954: ba byung lnga yis byug pa yis //
NG0249:1955: phyi yi mchod pa dag tu shes //
NG0249:1956: bdud rtsi lnga yi sbyor bas ni //
NG0249:1957: chag chag gdab cing las bya'o //
NG0249:1958: dam rdzas bdud rtsi ye shes lnga //
NG0249:1959: rak+ta'i chag chag gdab pa'i dgu //
NG0249:1963: a mr-i las kyi sbyor ba'o //
NG0249:1964: dam rdzas ye shes lnga ldan pas //
NG0249:1965: gsang mchog bsgrub phyir chag chag gdab //
NG0249:1967: ye shes lha yi bzhugs gnas te //
NG0249:1968: gnyis med mnyam pa'i dbyings su gdab par bya'o //
NG0249:1969: zla gam dmar po'i gzhal yas su //
NG0249:1970: gnyis med sbyor ba'i ngo bo las //
NG0249:1971: thugs rje chen po'i chags pa'i phul byung babs //
NG0249:1972: dbang gi rgyal po yab yum bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NG0249:1973: ra ga pu dza sa ma ye /
NG0249:1974: mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs shing gdab pa'o //
NG0249:1975: de nas yab yum gnyis su med pa'i mkha' dbyings nas //
NG0249:1976: byang chub sems kyi thig le 'debs //
NG0249:1978: tshon gyi rnam pa lnga po yang *//
NG0249:1979: yi ge dpa' bo 'bru lnga yis //
NG0249:1980: rin chen phye mar brlabs shing rigs kyi ngo bor gsal //
NG0249:1982: dang po phyi mtshams chen po ste //
NG0249:1983: rgyal po bzhi la las bcol mchod bstod bya //
NG0249:1984: bar gyi dbang po las bcol bstod //
NG0249:1985: mtshams su gnas pa'i las bya'o //
NG0249:1986: de nas rdzas rnams dgram pa ste //
NG0249:1987: phyi nang gsang ba gsum du shes so //
NG0249:1988: de nas lha bkod spyan drangs bstim //
NG0249:1989: byin brlab bkod cing snyan bstun gsol //
NG0249:1990: brtan par bzhugs shing 'dod don gsol //
NG0249:1991: dang po bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen bya //
NG0249:1992: de nas bsgrub pa dang ni bsgrub chen po //
NG0249:1993: de ltar las kyi rnam par bstan pa'o //
NG0249:1994: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:1995: sngon du 'gro ba'i rim pa bstan pa'i le'u ste so gnyis pa'o ///
NG0249:1996: / de nas yang pad+ma las kyis sems dpa' des /
NG0249:1997: dbang gi rgyal po la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:1998: bsnyen pa'i las rnams bstan du gsol //
NG0249:2000: dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0249:2001: nyon cig las kyi sems dpa' che //
NG0249:2002: legs par nyon la yid la zung *//
NG0249:2003: bsnyen pa'i las rnams bstan pa ni //
NG0249:2004: sku gsung thugs dang yon phrin las //
NG0249:2007: sngags kyi phreng ba 'bru brgyad gsal //
NG0249:2009: gnyis pa ma mo mkha' 'gro bskul //
NG0249:2010: gsum pa las kyi mkha' 'gro bsnyen //
NG0249:2011: zhi ba gnyis med ngang du bsnyen //
NG0249:2013: de las phar mchod tshur dngos grub //
NG0249:2015: de ni bsgrub pa chen po zhes //
NG0249:2016: phrin las bsgrub pa zhes bya ste //
NG0249:2017: gnas pa gnyen po bsten ni bsnyen pa ste //
NG0249:2019: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:2020: bsnyen bsgrub kyi le'u ste so gsum pa'o ///
NG0249:2021: / de nas yang pad+ma las kyi sems dpa' des /
NG0249:2022: bcom ldan 'das dbang gi rgyal po la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:2023: kye ma dbang mchog las kyi gtso //
NG0249:2024: gnan pa'i las rnams ba shad du gsol //
NG0249:2026: dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0249:2028: cig las kyi sems dpa' nyon //
NG0249:2029: mnan pa'i las rnams ngas bshad kyis //
NG0249:2030: kho nar nges par yid la zung *//
NG0249:2031: ma trang chen po bsgral ba la //
NG0249:2032: ma gos rtsod na nan pa ni / las mthar phyin gyis gnan pa'o //
NG0249:2033: de bzhin gnan pa'i las dag ni //
NG0249:2034: 'khor lo rtsibs ni brgyad pa bri //
NG0249:2035: dbus su yan lag nyid la gdang *//
NG0249:2036: mgo dang bcas pa'i gdong pa de //
NG0249:2037: dbang po lnga dang ldan par bri //
NG0249:2038: tha mar 'dzam bu gling gi dbyibs //
NG0249:2040: bkra mi shis pa'i thag pas bcing *//
NG0249:2041: gdug pa'i mtshon cha dang bcas pa //
NG0249:2042: sha khrag rdzas dang bcas pa bsham //
NG0249:2043: mon nam rabs chad thod par gzhug / yang na
NG0249:2044: ri gsum 'og tu gzhug / rgya mtsho'i ngogs dang
NG0249:2045: shing gcig gi / de ni gnan pa'i las su
NG0249:2046: shes // de ltar gnan na ldang mi 'gyur //
NG0249:2048: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las //
NG0249:2049: gnan pa'i le'u ste so bzhi pa'o //  // de nas yang pad+ma las kyi sems dpas /
NG0249:2050: bcom ldan 'das pad+ma dbang gi rgyal po la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:2051: kye ma bcom ldan gsang ba'i bdag / 'khor ba'i gdug pa ma lus dang *//
NG0249:2052: dregs chen ma lus 'dul ba'i tshe //
NG0249:2053: brtul zhugs spyod pa ji ltar bgyi //
NG0249:2054: lta ba ji ltar blta bar bgyi //
NG0249:2055: dam tshig ji ltar bsrung bar bgyi //
NG0249:2056: dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsol cig / ces gsol to //
NG0249:2057: dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0249:2058: las kyi sems dpa' zhu ba legs //
NG0249:2059: the tshom thams cad gcad par bya'o //
NG0249:2060: 'khor ba dag ni gdul ba'i tshe //
NG0249:2061: brtul zhugs spyod pa 'di ltar spyad //
NG0249:2062: lta ba blta ba 'di ltar blta //
NG0249:2063: bdag nyid ye shes khro bor brtag / 'khor ba bsgral ba'i zhing du blta //
NG0249:2064: dam tshig bsgral bar gsungs pa ste //
NG0249:2065: dam tshig bsgral ba chen po'o //
NG0249:2066: thogs rdug med pa'i brtul zhugs kyis //
NG0249:2067: the tshom med pa'i bsgral ba de //
NG0249:2068: brtul zhugs chen po 'di ltar spyad //
NG0249:2069: smyon pa'i chas su zhugs pa ni //
NG0249:2070: las dang ma lus bgrod kyang bgrod //
NG0249:2071: drag po'i las la smad mi bya //
NG0249:2072: lam mi gzur la phyag mi btsal //
NG0249:2073: phreng ba 'khar ba de bzhin gzung *//
NG0249:2074: khros pa'i cha lugs chen po yis //
NG0249:2076: kha mngar med pa zas su bza' //
NG0249:2077: gang dang 'phrad pa yang ni gnan cing brdeg par bya //
NG0249:2078: bang yang ngal dub med par rgyug / khros pa'i tshul gyis las rnams bya //
NG0249:2079: brtul zhugs bzhi yi chas su zhugs nas ni //
NG0249:2080: phyogs bzhir gdug pa'i nga ro gdon //
NG0249:2081: rta yi brtul zhugs chen po ni //
NG0249:2082: brjid pa'i tshul du byas nas ni //
NG0249:2083: mngar gsum mchongs shing nga ro gdon //
NG0249:2084: lag pa mdun dang rkang pa rgyab tu gdengs //
NG0249:2085: ngal dub med par 'dug gam 'chag / hrihlas rta mchog 'bar ba'i tshogs //
NG0249:2086: khro bo gdug pa'i nga ro gdengs //
NG0249:2087: rta mgo can gyis khams gsum @#//
NG0249:2090: rta mchog can yang char du 'bebs //
NG0249:2091: gdug pa'i tshogs la brdeg cing rgyug / 'di ni rta yi brtul zhugs yin //
NG0249:2092: khyi yi brtul zhugs drag 'bar te //
NG0249:2093: brjid pa gdug pa'i nga ro can //
NG0249:2094: g.yas pa lag gi 'du byed de //
NG0249:2095: g.yas pa brgyab brkyang mchongs pa'i tshul //
NG0249:2097: khro bo gdug pa'i nga ro gdengs //
NG0249:2098: khyi mgo can gyis khams gsum gang *//
NG0249:2099: gdug pa'i nga ro phyogs bcur sgrogs //
NG0249:2100: phyogs skyong rgyal rnams 'dar khrag skyugs //
NG0249:2101: ngal dub med pa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NG0249:2103: bya yi brtul zhugs chen po yi //
NG0249:2104: drag po brjid du ldan pa yis //
NG0249:2105: srid pa'i gdug pa bsgral ba de //
NG0249:2106: ku dang ye las bya mgo'i tshogs //
NG0249:2107: 'bar ba 'phros pas khams gsum spros bkang ste //
NG0249:2108: g.yas g.yon thabs dang shes rab gshog pa gdengs //
NG0249:2109: sngon du rdo rje sder mos bcum //
NG0249:2110: lding zhing rol pas rgyud drug sgrol la mkhas //
NG0249:2111: gdug pa ma lus bsgral ba'o //
NG0249:2112: phag gi brtul zhugs chen po ni //
NG0249:2113: gti mug 'joms pa'i phag rgod gdug pa'i sde //
NG0249:2114: du ru las ni phag gi tshogs //
NG0249:2115: khams gsum ma lus bkang byas te //
NG0249:2116: thams cad 'joms shing thams cad za //
NG0249:2117: gdug pa'i nga ro yongs su gdengs //
NG0249:2119: lag pa phag gi chang bar ldan //
NG0249:2120: phat kyis lcags ni rab tu 'phro //
NG0249:2122: dub dang ngal med rgyug la dga' //
NG0249:2123: khams gsum ma lus 'joms la dga' //
NG0249:2124: mi bzad sprul pa'i khro bo sprin dpung bzhin du spros //
NG0249:2125: dpa' bo ting 'dzin ldan pa yis //
NG0249:2126: thams cad 'joms shing gdug pa'i klu yi tshogs //
NG0249:2127: dpa' dang ldan pa'i ting 'dzin bya'o //
NG0249:2129: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:2130: brtul zhugs bzhi dka' thub smyon pa'i le'u ste so lnga pa'o ///
NG0249:2131: / de nas yang pad+ma las kyi sems dpa' des /
NG0249:2132: bcom ldan 'das dbang gi rgyal po la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:2133: kye ma bcom ldan gsang ba'i bdag / ma dad pa'i sems can chen po de bsgral ba ni /
NG0249:2134: rtsa rnam pa du zhig yod /
NG0249:2135: gar gyi dbang gis bshad du gsol //
NG0249:2137: dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0249:2138: pad+ma las kyi sems dpa' nyon cig / legs par nyon la yid la zung *//
NG0249:2139: ma dad sems can chen po la //
NG0249:2140: rtsa ni nyi khri chig stong ste //
NG0249:2141: de las sang sum brgya drug cu yod //
NG0249:2142: de las bsdus na rtsa chen gsum //
NG0249:2143: de las bsdu na rnam pa gnyis //
NG0249:2144: gcig ni bla yi rtsa ru gnas //
NG0249:2145: gcig ni dbugs kyi rtsa yin no //
NG0249:2148: rtsa chen gsum ni srog shing ste //
NG0249:2149: phung po lnga ni 'khor lo brtsegs pa bzhin //
NG0249:2152: de las yan lag bzhi gyes te //
NG0249:2154: lug bzhi khug gnyis lkugs pa ste //
NG0249:2155: gnas bzhir gzir cing sgo bzhir spung *//
NG0249:2156: rgyun lam gsum du gyen thur blta //
NG0249:2157: mthar byin lta bur byang chub sems //
NG0249:2158: de la dus dang sbyar zhing brtag / bla rtsa med na tsit+ta 'gas //
NG0249:2159: dbugs de dag dang 'grogs pa de //
NG0249:2160: de la drag dal yod pa'o //
NG0249:2161: rigs ni rnam pa bzhi yin te //
NG0249:2162: ring la dal la 'jam la ring *//
NG0249:2163: tshangs pa lha yi rigs yin te //
NG0249:2164: drag po myur ba srin po khro bo ste //
NG0249:2165: gdug pa 'dul ba dbang phyug tshangs pa ste //
NG0249:2166: gnyis min brtag par dka' ba dregs pa can gyi rigs //
NG0249:2167: de la dregs pa rnam pa dgu //
NG0249:2168: zhe sdang rang bzhin bdud du smin //
NG0249:2169: bdud ni ring la sngo ba'o //
NG0249:2170: nga rgyal las ni btsan du smin //
NG0249:2171: btsan ni thung la rtsub pa'o //
NG0249:2172: gti mug rgyal po chen po ste //
NG0249:2173: dal ba dang ni sdod du bcas //
NG0249:2174: 'phar dang sdod du thung ba dang *//
NG0249:2175: phrad la phra ba the brang ste //
NG0249:2176: de ltar brtag cing rab tu brtag / de ni ma dad sems can no //
NG0249:2178: rta mchog rol pa'i tan+t+ra las /
NG0249:2179: ma dad pa'i gnas dang phyi rabs don du rtsa'i dmigs bstan pa'i le'u ste so drug pa'o ///
NG0249:2180: / de nas yang las kyi sems dpas //
NG0249:2181: dbang gi rgyal po la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0249:2182: kye ma dbang gi rgyal po che //
NG0249:2183: bcom ldan gsang ba thugs rje'i bdag / phyi rabs rjes su 'jug pa yis //
NG0249:2184: lta ba ji ltar blta bar bgyi //
NG0249:2185: dbang gi rgyal pos bshad du gsol //
NG0249:2187: dbang gi rgyal pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0249:2188: nyon cig las kyi sems dpa' che //
NG0249:2189: lta ba dam pa ngas bshad kyis //
NG0249:2190: legs par nyon la yid la zung *//
NG0249:2191: byang chub sems ni rmad du byung *//
NG0249:2192: thams cad ma lus byang chub sems //
NG0249:2193: gang du yang ma sbas pas mthong ba nyid de mthong ba rmad du byung ba'o //
NG0249:2194: brjod du rdul tsam yang med pas kun tu khyab pa nyid de khyab pa rmad du byung ba'o //
NG0249:2195: ma shes 'khrul pa'i sems can kun ci yang shes
NG0249:2196: pas sems can te gnyis ka rmad du byung ba'o
NG0249:2197: // sems las bgrod du med pa'i mthar thug pas rmad du byung ba'o //
NG0249:2198: chos thams cad bsgom du med pa ste bsgom pa rmad du byung ba'o //
